name: Human Male
flavor_text: People say only ____ and smoke like high places. But as you can see, I love heights. Whenever I hear someone talk about a tower, I get an irresistible urge to climb it.

name: Human Male
flavor_text: Thirty years... Instant noodles only take 3 minutes, but I've waited 30 years! My mind and body have become weak, but now that I've been summoned, I'm going on a rampage thirty years in the making!
gacha_text: I'm going on a rampage thirty years in the making!
gacha_serif1:
Bandit: Who said you could enter!
SQEX: I did!

name: Human Female
flavor_text: I've got this! Climbing towers is a piece of cake for me. It's also pretty normal to see a big baddy at the top. Even if I were to be knocked off the tower, I'd just climb right back up. The only way to defeat a tower is to take it down one floor at a time.

name: Human Female
flavor_text: So this is how I look in color. I dig it! In black and white, fashion was so boring. And I couldn't tell if it was hot or cold! So inconvenient. I'm done with that now!
gacha_text: I still dream in black and white. I wonder if I'll start dreaming in color soon?
gacha_serif1:
Who are you?
SQEX: You keep out of it.

name: Esper Girl
flavor_text: People often mistake me for a mage, but I'm an esper. Mages are all old men, right? But if you just look at me, I'm a young girl. So... Esper, not mage. Got it?

name: Esper Girl
flavor_text: It's my time to shine. Mind Blast! Telekinesis! Stench... Man, I need a new one to replace Stench. It's ruining my cuteness.
gacha_text: Teleport! ...Huh?
gacha_serif1:
SQEX...
SQEX: I won't be defeated midway like these guys! Just watch!

name: Creator
flavor_text: Congratulations! You are the first over these 30 years to make it through the SaGa worlds. Your return to my presence was not part of the plan, but I shall give you my blessing nevertheless.

name: Creator
flavor_text: Are you sure? How amusing... You are trying to pick a fight with me! Very well. Remember the greatness of my power!
gacha_text: How amusing... You are trying to pick a fight with me!
gacha_serif1: Very well. Remember the greatness of my power!

name: Mech
flavor_text: One Leopard 2 battle tank, one Undulator, three Power Suits, one Excalibur, one Sun Blade, and, of course, my self-maintenance mode. Mechs all have different definitions of strength, but all this gear should certainly make it so I can fight.
gacha_text: Do you know what a Leopard 2 is?

name: Sensei
flavor_text: Ok, hear me out. During The Final Fantasy Legend, I was a mere blob of slime, but in Final Fantasy Legend II, I became a "Sensei". I don't even know myself what status I will eventually achieve. Just be sure to remember me if I somehow become a god.

name: Sensei
flavor_text: I have finally been called. It is time to step away from the podium to save the world. Okay, I'll be off now. Do be sure to study in my absence. Rest assured, I shall be back soon.
gacha_text: We shall go together!
gacha_serif1: Sensei: I've decided to come along with you!

name: Sensei
flavor_text: I'm not training to be a fashion model or a princess or anything. But maintaining proper posture is good for your health and even combat.
gacha_text: Then I have to tell you this.
gacha_serif1: Sensei: So you're leaving...

name: Father
flavor_text: I didn't think I'd be away from home for so long. I'm sorry. I have to do this to save the world and also to protect you guys. I know it sounds selfish, but you have to understand.

name: Father
flavor_text: Evil will stop at nothing to destroy the world. We must work together to stop it. That's what the Guardians do. As individuals, we are weak. But together, we have the power to fight against evil.
gacha_text: Evil exists in every world.
gacha_serif1:
SQEX: Dad! Are you leaving again?
Father: Yep. Take care of Mom.

name: Goddess
flavor_text: Am I really that goddess-like? Oh, I see. I was just a system, but they call me Goddess. I was like, what's up with that? So I guess I am a goddess after all. Hee hee, I can't get enough of it!

name: Apollo
flavor_text: All I want is to spread the blessing of the MAGI across the world. I'm embarrassed that people call me a new god. If I really had the power of a god, this task would be easy.

name: Apollo
flavor_text: When all the MAGI have been gathered, the power of the old gods will return. Behold! Now is the time for the birth of a real god, Apollo!
gacha_text: I WILL become a god!
gacha_serif1: Apollo: We welcome you, the hero of the world. I'd like to show my gratitude for defeating Ashura!

name: Haniwa
flavor_text: It looks like one of those terracotta clay figures called the haniwa. Whether this creature is really a haniwa or not, nobody knows. To call it a "haniwa-like thing" would be too confusing, so let's just call it Haniwa.

name: Albert
flavor_text: The hardest part about being left-handed is the fact that most weapons and armor are made for right-handed individuals. You right-handers probably won't understand the difference.

name: Albert
flavor_text: Bestowed the title of knight, I must live up to the frame of mind instilled in me by the chivalric order. While a heavy burden at times, I cannot abandon it. After all, I am the son of Rudolf, Marquis of Isthmus.
gacha_text:
I don't want to do anything
that would bring shame upon the aristocracy
of Rosalia.

name: Albert
flavor_text: I'm acutely aware that my appearance isn't befitting of a knight. But everyone told me this sort of attire is necessary on the Holy Night, so what other choice did I have? I consider this part of my sworn duty as well.
gacha_text: But what are we doing here? Do you need help with something?
gacha_serif1: A gift for you, from Polka.

name: Albert
flavor_text: I'm stronger than Sister believes. Yet as I am now, I'm useless to Prince Neidhart. I need more experience, more training.

name: Albert
flavor_text: Only a select few can undertake the trials of the gods. The path is closed to those blinded by lust and envy, and while harrowing, it promises a great reward.
gacha_text: Is that not fate?
gacha_serif1: Got Main Gauche!

name: Albert
flavor_text: What drives me forward is the hearts of those who hope for a joyous tomorrow. I must move forward even if it be at a crawl. Should I fall, another will surely take up my mantle.
gacha_text: I believe there is a light shining over all people.
gacha_serif1: I made a pledge to the prince! I won't bring dishonor upon the nobles of Rosalia!
gacha_serif2: I'm a Rose Knight, too! I wouldn't run off without you. Come, we fight together!

name: Jamil
flavor_text: Speed's everything to a thief. You won't even see me coming!

name: Jamil
flavor_text: Bam! Striking when and where you least expect it. That's a phantom thief. Surprised, aren't you? You better be surprised!

name: Jamil
flavor_text: I care not whom you see sitting on the throne. Estamir has only one true ruler. And now you too seek my help, yes? Then kneel. Kneel before your king.
gacha_text: ...I do not forgive...

name: Jamil
flavor_text: I'm so sleepy... Was up so late working. Stupid sun! Who needs it?! Ugh, so tired... How can anyone like summer? Oh, Farah, where are you? I'm about to dry up!
gacha_text:
Now's not the time
to worry about me.
gacha_serif1: Don't puke underwater! Keep it down!

name: Jamil
flavor_text: I used to struggle every day for pennies just to make a living. I'm done with that. The rules of this world are about to change. A thief like me will be able to become a king. I will soon have both Estamir and Rosalia in the palm of my hands!
gacha_text: Thieves of the world unite!
gacha_serif1:
Great! (Give her some money.)
Not so good.
gacha_serif2: Jamil, how'd it go today?

name: Jamil
flavor_text: Some people live in such luxury while there are starving kids out there. This is common in Estamir, but I don't hate it. I get a kick out of overcoming unreasonable obstacles.
gacha_text: I get a kick out of overcoming unreasonable obstacles.
gacha_serif1: Look, Dowd. We're gonna take everything we can get our hands on.

name: Gray
flavor_text: To live freely, shackled by no one... This takes strength. Nothing is more absurd than to be a prisoner to fame or fortune. Good and evil, right and wrong... These too are merely obstacles to a free life.

name: Gray
flavor_text: There are tales of a cursed sword. A sword that contains the soul of its maker. Freeing the soul just might lift the curse, and grant one access to the full power of that blade.
gacha_text: Show your true self!

name: Gray
flavor_text: The start of a new year. I know we are not celebrating a birthday, or somebody's wedding, but there's nothing wrong with a drink or two. Besides, I won't ask you to join me. We each have our own way of starting a new year.
gacha_text:
The thing is, I hate
standing in lines.
Let's toss some coins
into the offering box.
gacha_serif1: Just be sure not to lodge your 10 aurum into anyone's head.

name: Gray
flavor_text: I tire of your bulk blocking my path. And since I cannot go around you, I will take on the lot of you. Ready yourselves!
gacha_text: Are you strong enough to fight alongside me?
gacha_serif1: He seems stuck up... But what a looker! I have to get him in the party!
gacha_serif2: They call me Gray.

name: Gray
flavor_text: The evil god has been sealed away once more, but the world seems to have remained unchanged. It is still filled with plots and greed. I want to free myself from it all. That freedom is all I desire.
gacha_text: I will follow your orders. But even so, I'm doing so of my own accord.
gacha_serif1: I think I'll hang around here for a while.

name: Gray
flavor_text: I received a letter from a man claiming to be an old acquaintance. It writes of a troublesome task. The reward doesn't matter, but I smell adventure. It's not just your average royal conspiracy, but rather a grand escapade.
gacha_text: It is also important to seize adventure. After all, it may alter your fate.

name: Hawke
flavor_text: All right, maties! Raise the sails! Full speed ahead! All that booty'll be slowing 'em down. But if you don't shape up, Butcher'll beat us to it. Come on, put your backs into it!

name: Hawke
flavor_text: I'm Captain Hawke, a pirate. Point being, I don't think I'll be much good to you on land. I'm no woodcutter either, so don't make me swing this thing too much.

name: Hawke
flavor_text: What? Didn't recognize me with this wild outfit? I've me a few different looks, but I'm still the same gallant Captain Hawke ye've come to know.
gacha_text: Let's do this, me mateys!

name: Hawke
flavor_text: What do ye think lies beyond the sea? A country we know nothing of with music we've never heard and dancers we've never seen. And above all, mountains of untold treasures!
gacha_text: We pirates be free! We take orders from no one!
gacha_serif1: Shut it, Butcher! Let's get this over with!
gacha_serif2: Hawke! Ye've finally made it, huh?

name: Aisha
flavor_text: Winter is a prelude to spring. Leaves fall so that buds may open once more. So don't be sad. Such is the circle of life.

name: Aisha
flavor_text: Wooow, look at all the butterflies. There must be a Faerie's Grove up ahead. Please, little ones, lead me to the grove.
gacha_text:
What?! You're getting into the
water? No peeking!

name: Aisha
flavor_text: Thank you for coming to my tent. No one will see me giving these to you here. I've never given anyone chocolates before, so I would've been embarrassed if other people saw me. I hope you'll take these as an expression of my feelings.

name: Aisha
flavor_text: I don't like hot water, so I don't bathe in it. But stirring the water with this plank of wood is fun! It's called yumomi. It cools the water to just the right temperature.
gacha_text: Is the water really that hot?
gacha_serif1: So this is a foot bath? I feel all warm and cozy. This is amazing.

name: Aisha
flavor_text: The future of the Taralian Tribe is ours to decide. We need not obey Rosalia nor Kjaraht any longer. I must become chief to work with the empire and the knights to thwart Kayakith's ambitions.
gacha_text: The future of the Taralian Tribe is ours to decide.
gacha_serif1: Monsters have begun to flood the Steppes of Galessa...

name: Claudia
flavor_text: This bow is for protecting the creatures here. It isn't a tool for hunting. Why have you come to this forest? If it's to hunt, then leave now. Otherwise I will not hesitate to take your life.

name: Claudia
flavor_text: There I was, deep in Mazewood, when I saw her, with her arrow trained directly at my heart. That, and her cold gaze made it clear that trespassers were not permitted.

name: Claudia
flavor_text: Sadly, I am not a part of this forest. I'm a freeloader, an outsider, I just don't belong here. I am the daughter of an emperor. So I will face my destiny as the Emperor's daughter.
gacha_text:
Sylvan! Brau!
So it's time to say
goodbye, huh...
gacha_serif1: Sylvan! Brau! Thank you, everyone... Thank you and farewell!

name: Claudia
flavor_text: To enter Mazewood is to lose one's way... I lived in safety and peace there, but when we met, my heart became lost with doubt. And it was that doubt that drew me out of the forest.
gacha_text:
I face the darkness now,
a destiny decreed by the gods.

name: Claudia
flavor_text: The woods here are no place for a man to sully. And I do not believe that you were looking for me. I was raised here. There's not a soul that would seek me.

name: Claudia
flavor_text: I love this outfit. It's called a yukata? It's not easy to tie, but all the ways you can tie it are fun. Looks like you're used to wearing it. Is my way strange?

name: Claudia
flavor_text: This watering hole is a haven for inhabitants of Mazewood. You may have wandered here by chance, but now that you have learned of it, you must not be allowed to leave.
gacha_text: The animals and birds love the water, too.
gacha_serif1: Are you familiar with this cave?

name: Claudia
flavor_text: The stability of the Bafal Empire must be maintained to provide the residents of Mazewood and Melvir with peace and safety. As such, I must go to Melvir's palace. I won't be returning to Mazewood.
gacha_text: I won't be returning to Mazewood.

name: Barbara
flavor_text: We dance, we sing, we survive off of meager tips and table scraps. We are a troupe of traveling entertainers short on money. But the feeling we put into every step is real. My mind and body are telling me to keep dancing.

name: Barbara
flavor_text: Who will accept my rose tonight? And will it be nothing more than a spark in some dalliance? Or is this the night I find my one true love? Whatever may happen, it all starts with this rose.
gacha_text: Oh, is it over already?

name: Barbara
flavor_text: Even the leaves on the ground dance when they feel my rhythm. They dance with passion, as if given new life.

name: Barbara
flavor_text: That's it, everyone, keep up with the beat. It's the same rhythm as my heartbeat! It makes my soul burn with passion! Keep clapping, everyone! Louder, louder!

name: Barbara
flavor_text: A formal waltz? A passionate tango? You'll lead, right? The rhythm of the dance will take us to a higher place. Just don't go ruining it by stepping on my toes.
gacha_text: Sure! And if you like it, maybe throw in a little extra?
gacha_serif1: Hey lady... You're a dancer, aren't you? How about a performance?

name: Barbara
flavor_text: Jamil is a thief and Hawke a pirate. They both have companions or organizations they belong to. I'm different. I only have dance and the people who like to watch me dance, so I will keep dancing.
gacha_text: I shall dance to immortalize this moment.
gacha_serif1: Marvelous!

name: Sif
flavor_text: You challenged me knowing I am a Valhallan warrior? Your weapon will shatter under a single blow of my axe.

name: Sif
flavor_text: It's time for a dance. A Valhallan dance to arouse my warrior spirit. Or perhaps a dance of death to commemorate your demise?
gacha_text: Huh, interesting!
gacha_serif1: Quite confident, aren't you? Then join me on my journey and let's see if you truly have what it takes.

name: Sif
flavor_text: I tried wearing a swimsuit, but I still don't understand why we need it. In Valhalland, we bathe in the nude. I don't see the point in wearing these small pieces of cloth.

name: Sif
flavor_text: You'll make proper use of me? Splendid. I am no longer satisfied battling monsters of Valhalland. I am Sif, a Valhallan, and I am at your service.

name: Sif
flavor_text: Basic fitness, especially running, is important. If your lower body is weak, you cannot wield a weapon properly. Mages don't need this? An unfit mage is dead weight. You must become the best of the best! Come, let's spar!
gacha_text: Stamina! It is the foundation of everything.

name: Sif
flavor_text: That straightforward gaze... You're just like the boy back then. Don't be mad! It's a compliment. To become an honorable knight and overcome the trials of the gods, you have the potential to achieve those feats. Sif the Valhallan says so.
gacha_text: Have you kept up with your training?
gacha_serif1: I am Sif, a Valhallan. What 'bout you?

name: Diana
flavor_text: When I was chosen by Prince Neidhart, I felt a kind of fear hanging over me rather than joy. I must face this fear. No, not face it... I must come to terms with it. With everything.

name: Diana
flavor_text: I am Rosen Ritter Diana. Carrying on the desire of the late founder of our nation, Rosa Reimann, I am here to conquer this land. It is considered an honor to die by my sword. Now, come at me with everything you have!

name: Diana
flavor_text: You didn't realize I had a swimsuit under this cape, did you? Even a Rose Knight needs a break every now and then. Spending time with you like this is such a rare opportunity.

name: Diana
flavor_text: I have to keep moving, or I get all antsy. Other than my long-lost brother, I feel like there is something else important I'm forgetting...
gacha_text: I'm looking for my long-lost brother.
gacha_serif1: That cry... It might be a dragon. I've got to help him escape.

name: Galahad
flavor_text: Look at this! The Ice Sword is in my possession at long last! Let's test it out, shall we? Then when you meet Death in the Netherworld, you can tell him just how remarkable it is.
gacha_text: Never! I would never part with it, no matter how much you give me.
gacha_serif1: At long last! I've gotten the Ice Sword!

name: Galahad
flavor_text: The Ice Sword can freeze the enemies it cuts, and cause immense damage to those weak to cold. But that's not all. It also lets a common swordsman like me use powerful cold attacks.
gacha_text: I just got it.
gacha_serif1: Galahad, old friend! It's been a while. That's the Ice Sword, isn't it?
gacha_serif2: Gray, good to see you again!

name: Myriam
flavor_text: Studying fire spells is a very worthwhile endeavor. I absolutely love it. But I'm fashion-conscious too. I want to hear people tell me how good I look. Balancing the two is not easy work.

name: Myriam
flavor_text: Defensive and support fire spells do exist, but it's all about attack spells, am I right? Whenever I encounter a highly flammable monster, I get sooo excited.
gacha_text:
This was a lot of fun.
We should do it again
sometime. Byeee!
gacha_serif1: You know what? Maybe I should head back to Estamir once in a while, too.

name: Myriam
flavor_text: I put on the requested costume. Imagine a dream where you see this and hear "Trick or Treat"! The following morning wouldn't be easy for you.

name: Myriam
flavor_text: That's it... Thaaat's it. Come closer. The more the merrier. Then I can roast all of you at once with my Bird of Flame.
gacha_text: You mean you're going to let a delicate young girl travel all by her lonesome?
gacha_serif1: By myself? Hah! It's fun to go solo sometimes, anyway...

name: Myriam
flavor_text: A flame has no set shape. It can take any form, be it an orb, pillar, or wall. The mage imagines the shape and determines the effect of the spell. Right now, I want the flame to be a vortex and consume everything!
gacha_text: This really was a lot of fun.
gacha_serif1: You want me to pair up with you? Oh well. I guess it beats going alone.

name: Guella Ha
flavor_text: Captain, it's extremely difficult for a geckling like me to decipher maps left by humans. But several sources lead me to believe it should be around here.

name: Guella Ha
flavor_text: What's next? Some treasure hunting? Going after Butcher? Attacking an Imperial merchant ship? Honing our skills exterminating some monsters might be good too. Just don't tell me we're jumping ship and heading back to land.

name: Guella Ha
flavor_text: Soon we will cross blades with the enemy. Whoever fights the best will get a special prize from the Captain himself--and we all know his word is his bond. Right, Captain?
gacha_text: I want to make friends with many humans.
gacha_serif1: You may call me Guella Ha. I am a geckling, born on Walon Isle.
gacha_serif2:
Whoa! A lizaaard! See ya later.
It's good to have a reptile friend.

name: Brau
flavor_text: Prepare a large barrel. Fill it with spring water one third of the way. Make sure it isn't too hot. Then, just leave out a polka dot towel, and wait patiently for the bear to appear!

name: Butcher
flavor_text: You're a smart one. You can drink the poison and go straight to hell, or follow my orders and find some treasure. The choice should be pretty obvious.

name: Butcher
flavor_text: Oi, take a look 'ere. Killed it wif one stab, I did. But careful: Treat 'em like fat pigs an' you'll get yer arm bit off. Anyhow, we're havin' a full course o' shark meat tonight!

name: Butcher
flavor_text: Takin' treasure and lives! Swashbucklin'! Now that's piratin'! Really, I be the last person who oughta be watchin' some young snot. That's a job for you, Hawke.
gacha_text: Takin' treasure and lives! Swashbucklin'! Now that's piratin'!

name: Neidhart
flavor_text: Many take this armor, dark as night, as a symbol of evil. This is my intention. I chose black to instill fear in all those who behold it. When my enemies come across this suit of armor on the battlefield, they run. This makes things much, much easier for me.

name: Neidhart
flavor_text: Of course I am aware that what you truly desire isn't such childish, saccharine confectionery. But today... today is a special day. Please accept these as a token of my affection.

name: Neidhart
flavor_text: Who will sacrifice themselves to the theater of war? I will grant you the honor of an audience with Death himself. No takers? Death will not go unsated!
gacha_text: I see. Then, I will strike like a demon.

name: Neidhart
flavor_text: Helping my longtime enemy, Kjaraht, and saving Estamir from the demons. We fight for justice. May Elore protect us. Follow me! I will lead the way!
gacha_text: Let's go!

name: Darque
flavor_text: I am the rightful heir to the Assassins' Guild, which once spread fear across Kjaraht. None can escape my assassin skills. Whether king or leader of knights, to disobey me is to spell your death.
gacha_text: By now, you'd have died three times over.
gacha_serif1: I will now attempt the most revered technique of assassins: revival from death!

name: Darque
flavor_text: The evil god's minions tried to operate under the name of the Assassins' Guild. I put a stop to their plans. As Guild Master, it is I who must maintain our honor. Assassins serve no one. Only the guild dominates us all.
gacha_text: As Guild Master, it is I who must maintain our honor.
gacha_serif1: Where... where am I?

name: Darque
flavor_text: I remember days of rigorous training. I remember fleeing after stealing some pocket change. I also remember a man begging for his life. Oh, and that person. Whenever I think about that person, my chest aches in sorrow. Who was that noble soul?

name: Silver
flavor_text: I gotta thank ya. I'm finally free from the Fatestone. Elore, I kept up me end of the deal! From now on, I'm livin' on me own terms! The Fatestone be yer problem now.
gacha_text:
The Fatestone be
yer problem now.
gacha_serif1: Elore, I kept up me end of the deal! From now on, I'm livin' on me own terms!

name: Silver
flavor_text: I'm the boss. You serve me. If that suits you, then you can join.
gacha_text:
I'm the boss.
You serve me.

name: Silver
flavor_text: If ye call yerself one of me pirates, this height shouldn't scare ye. I'll show ye how it's done. Jump after me with all yer might. Ye'll hang if ye don't! Here I go!
gacha_text: I want thrills!
gacha_serif1: Ain't it more excitin' if it's shrouded in mystery?

name: Strife
flavor_text: Power. That is all I need. Intricate schemes to deceive humans... All worthless. Obtaining ultimate power will give me dominion over all. When my power exceeds my master's, I will become the true God of Destruction.
gacha_text: Foolish of you to come this far...
gacha_serif1: Strife

name: Mirsa
flavor_text: Under the guidance of the gods, I became a knight to walk the righteous path. There may be a few more rules, but the feeling of satisfaction I feel in my soul is tremendous.

name: Mirsa
flavor_text: Evil gods, listen to the sound of my heart beat! The oath of a knight, compassion for the weak, and respect for all life... I must now abandon all these to show my true form. Thank you and good bye forever!
gacha_text: Evil gods, listen to the sound of my heart beat!
gacha_serif1: Sorceress Aldora! Lend me your power... Fight for me, I beg of you.

name: Mirsa
flavor_text: I have something to say to you all. Our greatest foe lies ahead, but I may not be able to help all of you. Thus, here I would like to express my gratitude and bid my farewell. Thank you. We shall meet again someday.
gacha_text: Thank you. We shall meet again someday.
gacha_serif1: ...All right. I promise.

name: Death
flavor_text: Death is a purification of the soul. Souls which are exhausted from a corrupt world can be reborn and find new life through death. So revere death for it brings the birth of all life.
gacha_text: Why has a mortal come here?
gacha_serif1: Forget it. Where is Saruin? I want more powerful weapons! Bring Galahad back to life!
gacha_serif2: Why would the living dare to come here?

name: Death
flavor_text: The Netherworld is no place for the living. If you die now, your sins will be forgiven. Otherwise, you will roam Purgatory for eternity. You will perish either way. A simple choice, yes?

name: Death
flavor_text: This is a trade. You must offer something of value. In the Netherworld, treasure and fame have no value; only souls do, and the value of each one is equal. Yours, a friend's, or any other person's will do.
gacha_text: It is yours for a price.
gacha_serif1: Death

name: Leon
flavor_text: My son Gerard inherited my abilities... my existence itself. So who does that make me now? Am I still Emperor of Varennes? Or am I a mere shell of an emperor? Please, I need to know.

name: Leon
flavor_text: The Varennes Empire is still recovering, and my sons are too young. If I don't lead my men, they will leave me. I must stand on the front line.

name: Leon
flavor_text: Whatever it takes, I must get him to use that Soulsteal of his. I will do everything in my power to stop Kzinssie.
gacha_text: Kzinssie... You won't get away with this.
gacha_serif1: Victor, I trust you to carry affairs in my stead.

name: Gerard
flavor_text: Even many at the Imperial Court in Avalon are mistaken, but these aren't pajamas. I wear this clothing as a constant reminder that I, still in training, am not yet a fully fledged warrior.

name: Gerard
flavor_text: I gave up a life of my own, sacrificing everything in the fight against the Seven Heroes. I then passed on everything I learned from that fight. My life is not mine alone. This is the resolve necessary to become an Inheritor.
gacha_text:
Now I sally forth into the
world. Please, Father, watch
over me...
gacha_serif1: Y-yes! I will!
gacha_serif2: Right now, you're not strong enough to win. Let me pass on my power to you. Take it and fight, alright?

name: Gerard
flavor_text: When I inherited everything from my father, I also came to know of the hopes, disappointments and resignations he felt toward me. While this was a painful experience, above all I felt his love. It left me in tears. This love is the one thing I must pass on.
gacha_text:
Father... Brother...
I have
avenged you.
gacha_serif1:
Victor Canal, huh...?
Alright, we're heading to South Varennes!

name: Gerard
flavor_text: The Varennes Empire needs us all. We must not become attached to the throne of Avalon. That is the will I inherited from my father. I'm sure my successors will follow the same path.
gacha_text: The Varennes Empire needs us all.
gacha_serif1: I can't just sit here in Avalon doing nothing. Tell me everything you know.

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: The Imperial Throne has been passed on for generations. It contains all the aspirations of past emperors. This is what it means to sit on the throne. Should I fail, all those aspirations come to naught. This heavy burden must be converted to action.
gacha_text:
But please, stop calling me
Your Majesty. I am not
the Emperor anymore.

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: I am the last Inheritor. So I cannot cede the Imperial Throne to you. This confectionery is not intended to make up for this. In place of the throne, I offer myself, for your sake. This is a symbol of that.
gacha_text: Please continue to support the emperors...
gacha_serif1: ...Thank you. Please continue to support the emperors...

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: It is tradition to offer a dance to the gods at the start of a year. That duty was given to me. I am the Final Emperor, after all. What say have I in the matter?

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: To the termites who have long nested beneath Avalon, I must admire your will to survive. But I rule over Avalon, and you will not have this land!
gacha_text: You mean to tell me someone summoned these termites?
gacha_serif1: Y-your Majesty... Ungh...

name: Final Empress
flavor_text: When it comes to proper attire, what befits the Empress of Varennes more than battle gear? That said, as today is a day of celebration, I at least want to not look like a brute...
gacha_text: Be proud. Your very existence is a wonderful thing.

name: Final Empress
flavor_text: If the Rise of Morastrum takes the Sun and uses its power of life for death, then I'll use the grace of the Moon to make a new power of life and deliver the world from darkness!
gacha_text: I believe that even when times are hard, the power we need will rise up from within.
gacha_serif1: I've saved up my pocket money little by little.

name: Final Empress
flavor_text: Before my succession, I would spend my summer days at the beach. Only now do I realize how special such times were, even though I took them as a matter of course at the time. Thus, I want to cherish today to have no fears, even if tomorrow I must face the decisive battle.
gacha_text: I feel somewhat self-conscious walking down the street.
gacha_serif1: How can I disregard Miss Silver's invitation when you're such a kind-hearted person?

name: Coppelia
flavor_text: Wahahaha! I'm finally free from that geezer Hiraga. From now on, I'm doing my own thing. And you! Yeah, you! Don't tell me what to do!

name: Coppelia
flavor_text: I am Coppelia, Empress of Varennes. I have been rebooted and summoned here to fight once more. So, shall we dance?
gacha_text: I am the Empress now.

name: Coppelia
flavor_text: Did you think an automaton that doesn't breathe couldn't play the trumpet? Ignoramus! That geezer Hiraga installed an air pouch in me. Now, witness my transcendental performance and weep!
gacha_text: Boo ba bah, boo bah bah, boo ba bah, boo ba bah, boo bah bah baaah!
gacha_serif1: I don't know how to play either. I'm just here for the money.

name: Victor
flavor_text: This is my finisher, Flowing Slash. It damages an enemy's arms, and also lowers their Strength. That being said, most enemies are either defeated or brought down by the attack itself, so I've never actually seen the lowering effect in action.

name: Victor
flavor_text: Attacking me from behind, and with arrows, no less? Rapid Volley, Chaos Shot, Fusillade, Volley of Execution, Millionaire! These attacks are such cowardice!

name: Victor
flavor_text: There's nothing to worry about. I will protect you. Use everything you've got. Even if I fall, it means I can see Mother again... if it comes to that.

name: Victor
flavor_text: Kids running all about. Shopkeepers and customers haggling heatedly outside the stores. There are old men who worry about the future of the empire, as there are lovers who are lost in conversation. Indeed, this is none other than Avalon.
gacha_text: I just love a city where people can live free and be happy.
gacha_serif1: Father. Welcome back.

name: Sekishusai
flavor_text: I'm a clumsy man. I've become a stone boat in the face of the changing tides of time. The future is in your hands. Let this old man at least pave the path for you.

name: James
flavor_text: I am a soldier in the Imperial Army. I am prepared to do things mercenary warriors will not, like risking my life to complete my mission.

name: Liza
flavor_text: The Imperial Light Infantry tend to be looked down upon because of, well, the "light" part. But this is a grave mistake. Our attacks, defenses and mobility are designed to adapt to the conditions of any mission.

name: Therese
flavor_text: I can't miss at this range. How do I know that? Years of blood, sweat, and tears from intense training. Do you think I'm bluffing? Just try me.

name: Therese
flavor_text: Most rangers of the empire started out as true hunters. We are not only skilled in both archery and swordsmanship, we are also always training our abilities to track footprints and sense danger. Once you are in our grasp, there is no escape.
gacha_text: The city dulls my sense of smell.
gacha_serif1: Rapid Volley!

name: Emerald
flavor_text: I've always had a natural talent for Fire Arts. It's my destiny to study them... to wield them. I have no reason to doubt this.

name: Emerald
flavor_text: I seek more powerful spells, and more perfect control over fire... There's no end to my research into spells. One day, I will master the secrets of the Fire Arts.
gacha_text:
Take me with you!
I'm really good
with Fire Arts!
gacha_serif1: Well then, allow me to teach you Fireball.

name: Emerald
flavor_text: I am tireless in my studies of the Fire Arts. I even read ancient sorcery books in bed. Other kinds of spells? I might study those as well. Hehe...

name: Hector
flavor_text: Let me do my own thing. That's how I work. For instance, you look like you have something to say about my amazing hair. Go right ahead. You can even be blunt. See, most people wouldn't tell you that. But that... that is me doing my own thing.
gacha_text: We were hired under Lord Leon.
gacha_serif1: There's no reason to follow Lord Gerard.

name: Hector
flavor_text: Check out this lion mask. Suits me perfectly, huh? I love this design, but really, anything with a lion on it gets me fired up. I'm wearing it again this year!
gacha_text:
Tsk. I just had this made too,
and now it's ruined.
gacha_serif1: Hey, Polka. That's not worth a single aurum.

name: Hector
flavor_text: Your heart's desires! Your feelings! Say them loud and proud! Mercena-a-a-ry! Strength and power! Self-renewal! Evasion and counter! Bring 'em all on!
gacha_text: It is important that you sing with your very soul.

name: Orion
flavor_text: Conventional approaches? Precedents? Traditions? I'm going to turn all those on their heads. I am free. And with my power, I am going to change the world.

name: Andromache
flavor_text: Men, women... Such distinctions are meaningless. But still, for a woman to become a warrior, she must have indomitable beliefs.

name: Penelope
flavor_text: Chord progression? Syncopation? Those don't matter. I like to be free. I play what I desire. Let your feelings guide you and play!
gacha_text: I like freedom. I play what I desire.
gacha_serif1: My only skill is that of the sword, but I can do anything I set my mind to.

name: Wallenstein
flavor_text: It is my duty to preserve the glory of His Imperial Majesty. To that end, I will utilize all I have. My wits, my strength, my experience. Everything.

name: Hannibal
flavor_text: Strength, endurance, willpower. Only those who excel in all three can become an Imperial Guard and stand beside the emperor. We never falter, no matter the foe.
gacha_text: At your command, we shall claim victory!
gacha_serif1: I'm Hannibal. Nice to meet ya!
gacha_serif2: Your Majesty. I'm skilled with a spear. Please take me with you!

name: Hannibal
flavor_text: I will be there to protect the Imperial Majesty at all times. Such is the pride of the Imperial Guard. It is my duty to follow the Imperial Majesty, whether it be during a midwinter ski or a summer trip to the beach.
gacha_text: Don't go drowning now.
gacha_serif1: I am Her Highness's vassal. I don't listen to your orders.

name: Minerva
flavor_text: You confront me despite knowing I am Minerva of the Imperial Guard? You have pluck. Very well, then. I shall grant you the quick death you seem to desire.

name: Bear
flavor_text: The Imperial Heavy Infantry form an impenetrable barrier. One that keeps any attack or advance in check. Know that unless you defeat every last one of us, you shall not pass.

name: Bear
flavor_text: Yeah, I'm a bit of a blockhead. Don't expect me to be agile or think on my feet. But we have never retreated to the rear of the army. We will defend our position to our very last breath. That's what heavy infantry do.
gacha_text: Nice and slow now.
gacha_serif1: Parry!

name: Shiyuan
flavor_text: What am I drinking at this hour? Why, it's what you're thinking it is. And the more I drink, the more clearly I can think. Do you wish to join me? Naturally I will have to verify your age first.

name: Kongming
flavor_text: It is a great mistake to assume that a strategist always has a trick up his sleeve. I will, however, show you one trick of mine.
gacha_text: Manual labor isn't my forte.
gacha_serif1: This is a trap, Your Majesty.

name: Jubei
flavor_text: One must be ready to draw one's sword at any moment. However, the body cannot hold up if the mind is constantly on edge. Relax your mind, but be ready to act if needed. That is what it means to be alert.

name: Jubei
flavor_text: Wagnas, one of the Seven Heroes, destroyed our country and stole the pride of its people. To reclaim that pride, we chose to serve the Emperor of Avalon. We are the Levante Guard.
gacha_text: To serve a country is to care for the people.
gacha_serif1: I see. Then, serve me well!
gacha_serif2: It was his dying wish that I serve you in his absence, your Imperial Majesty.

name: Souji
flavor_text: I do not have long to live. I realize this all too well. Were I to die tomorrow morning, I would have no regrets, but at the end of each day, I am grateful for having lived another. I live my days calm at mind and prepared for the inevitable.

name: Sharrkan
flavor_text: Facing the desert dries your very spirit. The people of the desert are always looking to stay hydrated, both physically and spiritually. I never want to see a completely arid desert.

name: Jeanne
flavor_text: Men cannot be trusted. Not my father, my husband, nor my son. Relationships and vows matter not. Men, be gone!

name: Nomad Fatima
flavor_text: I use my bow and arrows to protect the sheep and horses. I don't like to take aim at another person, but I'm also not one to turn a blind eye to thievery either.

name: Georg
flavor_text: We have pledged our loyalty and our swords to His Imperial Majesty. All who would do wrong against the Empire shall receive the judgment of our Holy Blades!

name: Georg
flavor_text: I intend to carry the future of this nation on my back. It is my duty. However, while I watched my younger brother Thomas be born and grow up without any hardships, I suddenly found myself asking my father to allow me to join the knights so that I might train.
gacha_text: You will serve your country as king.
gacha_serif1: Tom, much has happened along the way, but you are now the king.

name: Sophia
flavor_text: Envisioning a peaceful world free from conflict, in which everyone can pursue happiness. This is what gives us Crusaders our strength.
gacha_text:
The Crusaders will assist in the
Empire's battles.
gacha_serif1: Thank you, Your Majesty. At long last, our battle is finally over.

name: Sophia
flavor_text: This is the, umm... proper attire of the Crusaders. For when we spend that special night with that special someone.

name: Sophia
flavor_text: A beautiful flower can have many effects on the human heart. It can heal, calm, provide joy, and give courage. Huh? No, I am no flower. I'm just a girl.
gacha_text: I only wish to be like a beautiful flower and heal the hearts of others.
gacha_serif1: Thank you for coming. I am Sophia, daughter of King Harold of Cumberland.

name: Agatha
flavor_text: The true strength of the Crusaders is demonstrated not by weaponry, but spells. Now, I will unleash all of my power.

name: Mariah
flavor_text: Another big catch today. The water is my friend, so I can always count on its grace. Do I feel guilty at all? One day, my life will return to the ocean, and I'll become a part of everything in it. This is just how things go.

name: Mariah
flavor_text: Seaweed thick as forests, coral sparkling like gems... You can learn plenty of important things just by living in the ocean.

name: Henrique
flavor_text: We're sophisticated gentlemen. Please do tell me which part of us makes ye think "pirates."

name: Eirik
flavor_text: We don't keep mu as pets. One mu supports an entire family. The life of a mu is more important than anything else. We risk our lives to keep them safe. Even if it's "only" a calf.

name: Karl
flavor_text: To transform one's body into a weapon and armor, only intense training will do. This is why we created the Dragon Lair. If this interests you, we welcome you anytime.

name: Terry
flavor_text: I was born on the Great Plains. I embarked into the Dragon's Lair to learn the essence of combat, but my heart never left home. You can't tie down a soul of the Great Plains!
gacha_text:
You can't tie down
a soul of the
Great Plains!
gacha_serif1: Dual Gunner!

name: Cat
flavor_text: Mr. Emperor is asleep, isn't he? Now it's time for the fun to begin. The moon's super bright tonight, though, so we gotta be careful. Now, what should we take?

name: Cat
flavor_text: Thought I was some kinda cute kitten who'd be easy prey? The thing about a cat's claws is... they're sharp, they dig in, and they hurt so bad you'll be crying for your momma. Here they come!
gacha_text:
If you need my services, ask for
the kitty cat.
gacha_serif1: Good night, Mister Emperor!

name: Cat
flavor_text: Normally I'm the one receiving the presents, but tonight I'm giving them out. It doesn't matter if you've been naughty or nice, take whatever you like. Santa Claws ain't stingy.

name: Cat
flavor_text: What do you think? Pretty light and airy, no? I feel like a cat who's shed her winter coat. Ooh, someone left a window open for me! Time to make some coin!
gacha_text: I'll handle it!
gacha_serif1: Hehehe...

name: Cat
flavor_text: If you think I'm your everyday cute kitty cat, you're sorely mistaken! I'll tear your throat out with my claws! Now, gimme all your goodies! And I'm not a kid, so candy is not good enough!
gacha_text: Now, gimme all your goodies!
gacha_serif1: We cats live on the streets, and our fleet feet know no defeat!

name: Kelut
flavor_text: You just looked at me, didn't you? You're spellbound by my frills. It's fine, stare at me. That's what they're for, after all. What's the point of having them if people ignore them?

name: Awe
flavor_text: These neck frills are a mark of pride for Salamanders. When a Salamander says, "I swear on my frills," they've made an unbreakable vow.
gacha_text:
These neck frills
are a mark of pride
for Salamanders.
gacha_serif1: Skydrive!

name: Siero
flavor_text: We're always in the ground, so these glasses are for keeping dirt out of our eyes. Above ground, they work as sunglasses because it's too bright. I'm not a good swimmer either, so in that case they become goggles. I wonder what other uses they may have?

name: Siero
flavor_text: They take our people and our families and lay their eggs in us so their larvae can feed on our bodies. I shall never forget the pain-filled cries of desperation rising up from the soil.
gacha_text: Lower your guard and the termites will rise.
gacha_serif1: The termites took our homes. Many of my comrades fell victim to those termites...

name: Thetis
flavor_text: Just trust me, and you'll be okay. You'll breathe normally underwater in the lake. Here, take my hand. Come with me, deeper and deeper...

name: Thetis
flavor_text: Bring a Moonlight Comb. Bring a Moonlight Comb to purify the water of Lake Aqua!

name: Windie
flavor_text: Being able to fly is pretty amazing, huh? A privilege reserved for only a handful of creatures. We can even fly nonstop without taking a rest. The sky is a world just for us.

name: Windie
flavor_text: I wanted to give you your present before anyone else, so I flew straight over. Here you are.

name: Azami
flavor_text: You think my attire is too revealing for a female ninja? The most important thing to a ninja is armor that allows us to stay agile. It's not like I want to be the center of attention, or even have people looking at me.
gacha_text:
I'm sorry! I just acted on
impulse! Please forgive me!
gacha_serif1: I'll lure the monsters and you defeat them, Your Majesty! ...Hey, don't you think we make a pretty good pair?

name: Azami
flavor_text: Staying hidden is the basis of ninjutsu, but if you're spotted, you have no choice but to engage the enemy. So, there's a whole branch of ninjutsu dedicated to combat. Care to volunteer for a demonstration?

name: Azami
flavor_text: As promised, I'm returning your kindness and I'm dressed for the occasion. And don't worry about what I'm holding. This is a present too.

name: Azami
flavor_text: I'm not playing around, I'm training. To move freely through water. To stay under a long time. To appear helpless and create openings. You fell for it? You better hold your breath!
gacha_text:
A ninja hides in shadows,
her presence unknown.
I do not like the sun.
gacha_serif1: Hey, stories aside, can we find some shade?

name: Azami
flavor_text: I thought I was given a broom because you wanted me to sweep. I use ninjutsu, not magic! I can't fly with this thing! But it's okay, right? I look cute in any outfit so I can get away with it.
gacha_text: I told you I can't fly!
gacha_serif1: Yeah, I'm ready to toss out the trash standing in front of me.

name: Orieve
flavor_text: I may dance for a ceremony or listen to the decree of the heavens. Such is my duty. If it brings peace to the nation and its people, that is enough for me. But my one true wish is to be with Noel.
gacha_text: I may dance for a ceremony or listen to the decree of the heavens.

name: Hiraga
flavor_text: I am Hiraga XVIII. For generations, my family has produced gifted inventors. Our society, however, suffers from a lack of genius minds. I shall create inventions that will save the world.

name: Prince Thomas
flavor_text: I have to study harder to lead the people of Cumberland to prosperity. Even if disaster strikes the country, with wisdom we shall surely overcome it.

name: Vampire Lady
flavor_text: Look at me! Just look at me! Am I not stunning? I look like some young maiden. If you tell people how old I really am, I'm going to have to punish you.

name: Vampire Lady
flavor_text: You humans go on about love, yet 'tis naught but a game in the end? "My one and only" this and "Forever" that, yet your lives are so brief. Meaningless to an immortal like me.
gacha_text:
We all fade away to
nothing, eventually.
gacha_serif1: If you want me, just say so! I like it that way.

name: Vampire Lady
flavor_text: Hey, you there. We need to run a blood test on you. You've traveled, no? Been bitten by a mosquito? You might be infected and not know it! We need a lot of blood! Hehe!
gacha_text:
I'll have this dealt
with within three
minutes.
gacha_serif1: I mean, only our clothes have changed. Besides, this look's not bad. I like it.

name: Vampire Lady
flavor_text: I loathe the sun! So, I have a 100% UV protection spell. Now, I can enjoy the beach and scope out tonight's prey without concern! Everyone looks scrumptious! Oh, I can't wait!
gacha_text: I loathe the sun!
gacha_serif1: Maybe they're an extraordinarily cute, immortal vampire like me!

name: Sephira
flavor_text: This sword is a sword of judgment. It ends the lives of the wicked and never so much as harms the virtuous. So, to which category do you belong? Do you have the confidence to receive its judgment?

name: Sephira
flavor_text: I can whisper to the winds to guide you to whatever it is you seek. If you do not seek anything, the winds cannot lead the way.

name: Sephira
flavor_text: Don't I look adorable?! I often flourish my sword, but I'm not scary! *sigh* I wish I could wear this all the time.
gacha_text:
What's that... sweet
fragrance in the air?
gacha_serif1: I wouldn't call it a poison so much as some kind of... transformation potion?

name: Narwhal's Daughter
flavor_text: Sailors far and wide fear the Master of the Ocean. They made her in the image of a human: a chaste, young maiden to become the object of their desires. Bah! Feel the wrath of Narwhal!

name: Narwhal's Daughter
flavor_text: Ta-dah! I've taken the form of a human. This must be a dream, a dream come true. I'm going to forever enjoy this with my special someone. I hope I never wake up...
gacha_text: But, it's New Year's. A special day that comes around once a year.
gacha_serif1: But this is the world we live in now.

name: Wagnas
flavor_text: Look upon me. This is the fate of a hero. By relentlessly seeking power, the world became unbalanced. But I have no regrets. I will give everything to be the strongest of the Seven.

name: Wagnas
flavor_text: What is a hero? One whose praises are sung, even beyond their death? No. A true hero carries out his convictions, even without recognition. The Seven Heroes are true heroes.
gacha_text:
Welcome!
I take it you've been
enjoying yourselves?
gacha_serif1: Well, I'm sorry to hear that. But there's no time to make it up to you.

name: Wagnas
flavor_text: The end of the world draws near, but to ignore the imminent threat of the termites would result in our total extermination. We should be saving people first. Is that not the obvious choice?
gacha_text: We should be saving people first. Is that not the obvious choice?

name: Noel
flavor_text: I don't care for needless conflict. I'd prefer to talk things out. But if your mind is already made up, then there's no other choice, is there? Just know that I have no intention of handing you an easy victory.

name: Noel
flavor_text: Who did you defeat? You defeated a friend, with whom I was bound by blood. In other words, someone important to me. Now I will not hold back. I will kill you with the full extent of my power.
gacha_text: Do me a favor and let me kill you.
gacha_serif1: It's been a long time, Sagzaar.

name: Noel
flavor_text: I am a soldier. Soldiers exist solely to protect the people. But too many have lost their lives to you damn termites. So, I don't care what it is you are fighting for, I will not forgive you.
gacha_text: I don't care what it is you are fighting for, I will not forgive you.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: All I want to do is help my brother and Wagnas. To that end, I have many things I must accomplish. Enough of your babbling, and get out of my way!

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: Brother, Wagnas, I am going to fight now. Please watch over me!
gacha_text: You'll be fighting for me from now on.
gacha_serif1: I can tell that you're really strong. Can I ask you a favor?

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: You're not going to tell me you don't need it, right? Right?!
gacha_text:
Why do I have to wear this
anyway?
gacha_serif1: ...Really? I guess it's fine then.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: The one who can help Lord Wagnas is not I, but rather my brother, Lord Noel. The one Lord Wagnas first called for was not I, but Lord Noel. One day I hope I can serve Lord Wagnas, and be the one he requests first.
gacha_text: One day I hope I can serve Lord Wagnas, and be the one he requests first.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: This odd little Daruma is supposed to bring good fortune. You can see both of its eyes! You must be lucky. Here, come closer. Rejoice, for I'm gonna turn you into a Daruma, too.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: These little "squid" creatures are delectable. Such a waste to just kill them and not eat them. They're great fried or grilled, but I think they're best raw. From now on, I'll gulp them down alive. They should be grateful for my benevolence.
gacha_text: These little "squid" creatures are delectable.

name: Subier
flavor_text: I can handle the sea myself. I do not need your interference.

name: Subier
flavor_text: So, you've given me a calligraphy brush. All right, I'll write one word to express my hope for the new year: Sea!
gacha_text: The first calligraphy of the year! Exciting!
gacha_serif1: New Year's is great, and the drinks are free!

name: Dantarg
flavor_text: Don't even bother showing yourselves, you pathetic creatures. You're not even worthy enough for me to crush beneath my feet.

name: Dantarg
flavor_text: You dare stand before me? Very well. It's been a long time since I've had worthy adversaries. I'll crush you!
gacha_text:
You're in no position
to threaten me!
gacha_serif1:
Don't make me regret it.
As long as you continue to behave yourself here, I'll leave you alone, Dantarg.
gacha_serif2: What? Did I hear that right? You're just going to let me go?

name: Bokhohn
flavor_text: I am just a small fry. One look at me and that much should be obvious. So please, let me go.

name: Bokhohn
flavor_text: To emerge so nonchalantly at this stage... You clearly lack any strategy. Let us begin, then. Your mistake will be your downfall!
gacha_text:
Was it part of your plan to come
after me last?
gacha_serif1: You naive fool!

name: Kzinssie
flavor_text: I am Kzinssie of the Seven Heroes. The strongest of the Heroes. I am the strongest! If you fear me, then run. You wish to stay? Then you shall die. Soulsteal!

name: Kzinssie
flavor_text: I've always been strong. Wagnas and Noel were both scared to even look me in the eye. When they asked me to join the Seven Heroes, I felt generous and said yes.
gacha_text:
I was getting tired of waiting.
Let's start already!
gacha_serif1: A-again!

name: Julian
flavor_text: You might be wondering how capable I really am, but trust me, no one's more devoted to defending Sinon than me. This is where my younger sister was born and where she died.

name: Julian
flavor_text: You're probably thinking "Look at this weak pretty boy" or something, huh? Wanna say hi to my fist? We'll find out how weak this "pretty boy" really is.

name: Julian
flavor_text: I see you came dressed for the occasion. I did my best to clean up nicely too. Let's forget about who we usually are. Tonight, we can pretend to be cool, right?
gacha_text:
Lady Monika, it's freezing
out here. Could you maybe
make it quick?

name: Julian
flavor_text: Thanks for the chocolates. These are from me and are for you and you alone. Seriously, you really are the only one getting these. I'm no two-timer.

name: Julian
flavor_text: Me, in the Princess Guard! I knew Lord Mikhail recognized talent. I've earned Lady Monika's trust, too. These bigwigs, they're different. Ellen's sure to look at me in a new light!
gacha_text: No problem! I guess...

name: Julian
flavor_text: The wind has grown colder. Winter is coming. The cold is nice, but only when you have someone to keep you warm. I hope I can see the girls I met at the beach and that Slime girl again!
gacha_text: I hope I can see those girls again!

name: Thomas
flavor_text: To be a leader with the right attitude, always looking ahead, living up to expectations. Such is the duty of those born with the Bent family name. I've yet to become such a person. But one day I shall. This I swear on my family's name.

name: Thomas
flavor_text: If Loanne is once again under threat, then I too shall fight. There's nothing special about this. After all, we felt the same way the last time this happened.
gacha_text:
I hope our paths
will cross again.
gacha_serif1: I'm joining a newly formed escort squad for Lady Monika.
gacha_serif2: I'll be heading for Pidona now.

name: Thomas
flavor_text: Stone. Wood. Hides. Paper. What makes a book has changed, but they've always been an important vehicle for crafting the future of civilization. Read a book and transcend time!
gacha_text:
If there's anything I
can do... anything
at all.
gacha_serif1: Young Thomas. Thank you for coming. Welcome to Pidona.

name: Thomas
flavor_text: I've polished myself as much as a Bent can. There will come a time when I'll have to put it to the test, and I will learn my true worth. Yes, the time has come.
gacha_text: Life always finds a way to prevail!
gacha_serif1: Life always finds a way to prevail!

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: There are those who seek to depose me, to take over this country. This is a golden opportunity. I'll round up all of them, including my other detractors, and defeat them once and for all. Then, I'll unite Loanne under one banner. All before the Sinistrals return.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: Byunei's forces are marching on Loanne. I will lead the fight against them. The enemies will be routed. I will not let them lay a finger on the people of Loanne!
gacha_text:
Hmph. So be it.
Then follow me
to the ends of the Abyss!
gacha_serif1: There's no reason for you to risk your life, Khalid. Good work.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: This banquet is to celebrate everyone's achievements. Your attire is formal yet not overly extravagant, and your figure and demeanor are already perfect. And above all, you're beautiful... ly dressed, I mean.
gacha_text:
I wish you can
continue your efforts.
gacha_serif1: Last but not least, there's one other warrior whose splendid courage I wish to acknowledge.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: I will spare no effort and shed any blood to see Loanne become a greater, richer nation. I will not hesitate to resort to lesser means if necessary. I am not the Marquis of Loanne to uphold justice.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: Armor and formal attire is all for show. What I really need is a person I can trust. And that person is you. With you here, even like this, I feel at ease.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: Tornado? Some might call me that. With Khamsin in hand, I make it rain blood on any battlefield. That's what I do. I'm just a simple mercenary with a simple mission--to get paid.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: Everyone, lend me your strength! With it, I'll call a tornado and we'll smash the enemy in one fell swoop!
gacha_text:
Pass me the reins so that I
may lead us to glorious
victory. Soldiers, will you
follow me into battle?
gacha_serif1: Art thou Khamsin's successor?

name: Khalid
flavor_text: My father always dreamed I would marry a princess one day. With every one of my victories on the battlefield, my father pushed me to get better and better, all for her. I knew, though... that dream would never come true.
gacha_text:
I personally don't have
such ridiculous dreams.
gacha_serif1: But if this is Emelia's dream world, then I'm afraid I have no clue where she is.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: The Kingdom of Naj fell, and the surviving members of the Gessian royal family scattered across the world. I still cannot abandon the hope, however unlikely, that somewhere out there, the princess is alive.

name: Khalid
flavor_text: The true Khamsin is obtained by relinquishing what you hold dearest. That means the Khamsin has become more important to me than anything else. I have no regrets!
gacha_text: I have no regrets!
gacha_serif1: Princess! You're safe...

name: Sarah
flavor_text: The Child of Destiny... Desired by none, despised by all, cursed spreader of death and sower of discord, home to misfortune, destroyer of the world... Yes, I am that Child of Destiny.
gacha_text: You need not be afraid.
gacha_serif1: I can feel my life changing. I'm not the person I was yesterday!

name: Sarah
flavor_text: When my big sister isn't around, I sit amongst the flowers and insects. I think about many things. The present... The future... Things I can never tell Sis. Maybe I'm a bad child after all.
gacha_text: Ellen. I'm coming, too.
gacha_serif1: And I'm her sister, Sarah.

name: Sarah
flavor_text: I'm no good with words. I'm awful at saying thank you. I also struggle to comfort others. But surely the trill of my flute will reach the ears of children dejected or in pain.

name: Sarah
flavor_text: What matters isn't physical strength but heart and will. The will to survive, care for others, and yearn for happiness. With hearts as one, we will overcome the power of Oblivion. Come, let us band together.
gacha_text: It is MY responsibility to close the gate.
gacha_serif1: It is MY responsibility to close the gate. Not yours.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: This is my problem. I'll deal with it myself. I don't need any input from you. Got it?
gacha_text:
Well... we used to play house when
we were kids.
gacha_serif1: A lot of things wind up in Loanne. Want to go take a look together? We might as well buy something.
gacha_serif2: But you know, Julian, I don't think I could ever be your lover or anything.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Everyone tells me I seem like a natural in hand-to-hand combat, but personally, I prefer an axe. There's nothing like the thrill of swinging one around to your heart's content.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Why do I need to wear THIS just to give some chocolates? I feel so embarrassed...

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Maybe, I got a bit carried away packing. This thing's gonna crush me. The axe? Oh, that's no issue. It's basically a part of me.
gacha_text: Take care, Tom.
gacha_serif1: Ellen, I'd really like to go to Pidona with Tom.
gacha_serif2: What're ya on about? Tom, what's going on here?

name: Ellen
flavor_text: Even if what I see before me is the true form of the Sinistrals, what of it? I will defeat you and close the Abyss Gate. I'll never hand Sarah over to you!
gacha_text: I won't let you die!
gacha_serif1: Sarah... Let's go home.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: It peeves me that I'm seen as some savage woman who waves around an axe all day. A fashionable umbrella suits me just fine, thank you very much.
gacha_text: A fashionable umbrella suits me just fine, thank you very much.
gacha_serif1: If the ancient text Silver found is the real deal, then it's most definitely this island.

name: Ellen
flavor_text: I've stripped away the pointless extras and gone lighter. You're saying I stripped too much? Who told you I meant clothes?! I was talking about my AXE! I was wondering what you were eyeballing. You'll be the first victim of my new axe if you're not careful.

name: Monika
flavor_text: I want to help my brother and Loanne in any way I can. I know my way around a sword. You can count on me.

name: Monika
flavor_text: If there's any information I can provide, I'll tell you gladly. I don't know how much help I'll be, given many places are quite different after these 300 years, but I'll do my best to assist you however possible.
gacha_text:
Can you take my hand?
I don't feel
safe here in the dark.

name: Monika
flavor_text: You've been very good again this year, so I've brought you a present. I can't stay long, though, as I have to hit all the other villages in Loanne as well!
gacha_text:
I've decided! I would like to
bring Christmas joy to less
fortunate children around the world!

name: Monika
flavor_text: Today is the day to celebrate your great deeds. For this occasion, I chose a dress that I hope will convey my deep gratitude to you all.
gacha_text:
May the wind be in
Vanguard's favor.

name: Monika
flavor_text: I rode like the wind that night. It gave me the strength to face my destiny. I feel I will never lose heart, no matter how difficult the daily battles I face, for my heart has sprouted wings and I can fly freely like a bird.
gacha_text: Brother has permitted me to get out and about.
gacha_serif1: So warm.

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Sized me up the moment you saw me, didn't you? Me and my weapon. Well, now I'll show you who I really am. Masquerade!

name: Katarina
flavor_text: There isn't a moment to waste. I will take care of things here. You should go on ahead.
gacha_text:
I will return with the
Masquerade in hand.
gacha_serif1: Lord... Mikhail... I'm so... happy...

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Well, I'm another year older. So while it's not all good news, for now let's celebrate the year to come.
gacha_text:
You should quit while you're
ahead. It's bad luck if you
miss.
gacha_serif1: You don't look like you're in such good shape yourself.

name: Katarina
flavor_text: Everyone probably suspects I cut my hair out of the shame I felt toward Lord Mikhail. But they're wrong. A wild delusion became reality, and I got carried away. I needed to let that go.
gacha_text: You take care as well, Milady.
gacha_serif1: Katarina... What happened to your hair?!

name: Katarina
flavor_text: The Marquis gave me this dagger known as Masquerade. I've concealed it within my dress so that I can stay close to and guard Lady Monika. However, I will need more than a dagger to defend against this foe. It is time to reveal Masquerade's true form.
gacha_text: Please allow me a chance to take back Masquerade.
gacha_serif1: Katarina, do you have the Masquerade on your person?
gacha_serif2: Yes, right here.

name: Katarina
flavor_text: I can't give you my name or discuss my past. Have you heard of any rumors surrounding a special small sword? What of a great sword? Well... do you know of a man who goes about bragging about deceiving women?

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: So yeah, um, you can call me Santa. And this teddy bear isn't a present, so don't get the wrong idea. If anything, I'm out looking for presents for myself! Got anything for me?

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: Gotcha! Come on, forget studying. Let's go play!

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: Heehee. Come on, take me somewhere. I'm, uh... Eclair. Oh, you've heard that name before? Then call me Bavarois. No, wait, Mille Feuille. Oh, call me anything you like!
gacha_text:
I caught you,
so no running away!
gacha_serif1: Oh! I'm, uh... Eclair.
gacha_serif2: Guess we got no choice. So what's your name?

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: You must think I'm a child who has had an extremely unlucky lot in life. But I've had so much fun visiting all the places in the world. I've not only met all sorts of people, but I'm also lucky enough to have come to a world like this. Where I came from is not important at all.
gacha_text: I wonder who would be the most fun to follow around.
gacha_serif1: No.

name: Muse
flavor_text: Holding a grudge over what happened to my father won't do me any good at all. I would rather live alongside others, enjoying every day. Tomorrow will be another good day. I want to go through life always believing this.

name: Muse
flavor_text: I pray for the return of peace and serenity to the world; for the happiness of the people of Pidona; and for the safe return of Charl and his allies. Charl... I pray I can see your warm smile once more.
gacha_text: I pray that you may have a quiet and peaceful life.
gacha_serif1: Look! Lady Muse is awake!

name: Charl
flavor_text: The Silver Glove, a relic of the Matriarch, was hidden in a dream world. Am I qualified to inherit such an object? And who am I supposed to protect with it?

name: Charl
flavor_text: I can still use the Shucho Arts without the Silver Glove. But if I collect two of them, I would regain all the abilities I once had.
gacha_text:
...Khalid. I need to borrow the
Silver Glove.
gacha_serif1: The Silver Glove won't disappear!

name: Charl
flavor_text: I am not the Charl I once was. I am now protecting Lady Muse. That is my one and only desire.
gacha_text: It's my turn to lend a hand this time.
gacha_serif1: We will not leave you by yourself.

name: Nora
flavor_text: Whatever the era, being a weaponsmith is all I've ever known, so that's what I'm doing here too. And I can do a lot more now than I could back then. In any case, I just love to bang away!

name: Nora
flavor_text: Hey, this hammer isn't for bashing monsters. It's for forging the greatest weapons and armor there ever were. Aren't there any new weapons or armor out there which may give me inspiration?

name: Nora
flavor_text: Tougher monsters help get the blood flowing for some serious training. Weak opponents don't make you strong. Let's get a real workout today.
gacha_text: We're closed for the day!
gacha_serif1: I can't stay here, Cain. I gotta get even for the old man and find the Spear. Look after the place for me.

name: Young Boy
flavor_text: I have forgotten when exactly I learned I was a Child of Destiny. Life was easier once I knew. My whole fate is all preordained, and nothing can change it. I'll just accept what happens until fate sees fit to end me.
gacha_text: Just leave me alone!
gacha_serif1: Just leave me alone!

name: Robin
flavor_text: Hahahaha! Know this, evil is always lurking in the dark corners of society! The day has eyes, the night has ears, but Robin the Crusader has both!

name: Robin
flavor_text: The residents of Yarmouth are free. The people there... they smile. All of them. Seeing the joy on their faces gives me the energy to keep doing what I do.

name: Robin
flavor_text: So evildoers do not learn my true identity? So my fans do not hound me while I'm off-duty? No, I just don't want my father to know. That's the only reason.

name: Robin
flavor_text: Titles, medals... No matter what they award me, I can't reveal my true identity. Besides, I'm not doing this for fame. Your wonderful smiles are all I need!
gacha_text:
A hero who fights for
justice doesn't reveal his
identity. That's the rule!

name: Robin (Fake)
flavor_text: Evil stands no chance when Robin the Crusader is around! Why do you look so skeptical? My physique, my graceful moves... and check out this costume! I am the real deal!

name: Robin (Fake)
flavor_text: The Masked Crusader's secrets? They're all right here in my belly! What, you don't believe me? I have many secrets. That's why my belly's so big! Bwahahaha! See ya!
gacha_text:
Hey guys,
can I help?

name: Robin (Fake)
flavor_text: They say my double has been showing up a lot. What I don't get is how he's fooling everyone. I mean, look at me! Who else is this slick? This right here is bona fide Robin Style!

name: Ward
flavor_text: I'm in dire need of income. Will you take me with you on a gig, any gig, so I can make some money? It could be a monster-ridden pit for all I care. No matter the danger, as long as it's profitable, I'm in.

name: Ward
flavor_text: Even if you're poor, you should still mind your appearance. Forget that "it's what inside that counts" nonsense. A man should look sharp--especially if he doesn't have money.
gacha_text:
Do I look like
I have money?
gacha_serif1: You there. How'd you like to make some money?

name: Black
flavor_text: Listen up... If it be treasure, no matter where it be, it exists to be taken by ME. Ye heard me. It's aaall mine. I won't be giving ye bums one coin or one single gem!

name: Black
flavor_text: A famous pirate? Do ye know who stands before ye? The man who faced Forneus, the Abyss Lord of the Sea, twice -- and got his revenge! I be the living legend, Black the Pirate!
gacha_text: No way I'd forget!
gacha_serif1: Yer hair may be longer, but I'd never forget that face. What be this bilge about "Maximus"? Yer name be Jackal!

name: Black
flavor_text: I be used to transformations. So, as requested, I've become a werewolf. It be a full moon tonight. Time to cut loose.
gacha_text: It be a full moon tonight. Time to cut loose.
gacha_serif1: Ye surely suffered a serious shock to've forgotten Black the living legend.

name: Black
flavor_text: Me leg! Me youth! Me strength! They all be back! Slayin' Forneus really does break the curse. I feel the first tears I've ever cried in me life. Black the pirate be back!
gacha_text: Now I've me youth again, I'm unstoppable!
gacha_serif1: Now I've me youth again, I'm unstoppable!

name: Herman
flavor_text: That bastard Forneus took everything from me. Me leg, me strength, me treasure, me youth, me friends... I don't care if he be the "Abyss Lord of the Sea", or one of the Sinistrals, or whatever. I'll 'ave me revenge. I won't die until I do!

name: Fullbright XXIII
flavor_text: What helped the Matriarch achieve victory? Ferdinand's bravery? Vassault's wisdom? Nay! It was my ancestor Fullbright XII's economic might. Commerce drives all industries. I fear not Messina nor the Divine Order.
gacha_text: In my line of work, information is the most valuable thing.
gacha_serif1: So you must be Thomas. I'm Fullbright XXIII.

name: Zhi Ling
flavor_text: Spirits of heaven and earth, grant thy blessings today. We shall bestow thy blessing unto thee. Please endow us with what remains. If we break this vow, we offer thee our souls in return. Kindly bestow upon us thy blessings.

name: Zhi Ling
flavor_text: When taking aim at something, never think about what that thing is. Simply empty your mind, and gently loose your arrow. If your mind wavers, your arrow won't find its target.
gacha_text: Stop calling me "Lingling"!
gacha_serif1: You're...

name: Bai Meiniang
flavor_text: Needing help from an old fart like me tells me a lot about you Grave Knights. I do ask a favor in return. Here, I got this knot in my shoulder that just won't go away.
gacha_text:
Whaaat? I just want to
learn about the West.
That's all.
gacha_serif1: That "advisor" Tsao Gao is the one making the decisions. Those people in Huang are a bunch of dirtbags.

name: Boston
flavor_text: Hi, I'm Boston of the lobster tribe from World's End, an island at the edge of the world. At least once in your life, I suggest you come watch the sea flow to the depths beneath the island and feel its indescribable intensity.
gacha_text: Would you mind if I joined you on Vanguard?

name: Boston
flavor_text: These claws are the Lobster Clan's greatest weapon. Obvious, right? They're claws, so they pinch. That's what our enemy expects. And then, all of a sudden, we slam them! Crack open their skulls! That's how these claws are used right.
gacha_text: These claws are the Lobster Clan's greatest weapon.
gacha_serif1: Shenlong Firefist!

name: Faerie
flavor_text: Teehee. I'll shove this spear up evildoers' rears and twist 'til they squeal. Then I'll bash their heads and make 'em froth at the mouth. Come on, evildoers, this is gonna be fun!
gacha_text: I gotta pull a prank on someone.
gacha_serif1: Forgive me for not thanking you earlier. I appreciate you letting me go.

name: Faerie
flavor_text: I am Rocbouquet. Yield to temptation! Come on, swoon already. What? I'm too small to be Rocbouquet? Just cuz I'm a bit little... I worked hard on this! You're so mean!

name: Faerie
flavor_text: Whoa! I can't believe a human made it here. You didn't get lost? Well, since you're here, we'll make sure you enjoy your stay. These memories'll last you a lifetime, hehe.
gacha_text: I can't believe a human made it here. How'd you not get lost?

name: Rukh
flavor_text: Yes, I am an elephant. This world is filled with monsters. Surely an anthropomorphic elephant isn't that strange. Why do you look at me so? I get it... You've never seen an elephant before, have you? Then take a good look. For an elephant is what I am.

name: Rukh
flavor_text: I heard tales of creatures like Rukh with four legs. Are they like centaurs? They can't be walking on their hands, crawling everywhere. Ridiculous! We have two legs. Two!
gacha_text: Rukh only has and needs two legs.
gacha_serif1: Now that Big Bro's better, guess I'll head out and see the world.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: Who gives out presents on this holy night? A Snowman, of course! You thought it was an old man with a beard? Well, you're wrong. This kind of cold is dangerous for the elderly.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: I am a Snowman. One look at me and that much should be obvious. It is my Everfrost Crystal that prevents me from melting. This ensures you won't wake up to find a puddle of water in my place tomorrow morning.

name: Flurry
flavor_text: I am always serious. I never joke around. I wish people would stop smirking when they see my face. I can't help the way I was born. I wish everyone else were as serious as I am.
gacha_text:
You don't mind if I
take that, right?
gacha_serif1: No touching allowed.

name: Undine
flavor_text: You seem like you're up to the task, so I have a request, if you'll listen. Of course, I'll give you something in return. Money, or perhaps I can teach you the Genbu Arts, which I'm quite good at. I could teach you other magic as well, if that interests you.

name: Undine
flavor_text: The Genbu Arts control Water Spirits. I myself am a practitioner of Genbu, though I'm not as good as someone like Vassar. He got Vanguard off the ground, after all. One of the characteristics of Genbu is its balance between attack, defense and recovery.

name: Undine
flavor_text: Volcano... That boy is absolutely brimming with talent. It feels as though coming across him was destiny, but I could very well be creating my greatest enemy.
gacha_text:
Oh my, you're all such
cuties. I'm looking
forward to our class.
gacha_serif1: Volcano! Where did you...

name: Undine
flavor_text: You want to move Vanguard? I don't mind helping, but that'll be impossible right now with Volcano around. If only we could get him to leave Mahzoz...
gacha_text: To the south lives a crazed mage named Volcano. Snuff out this firebrand.
gacha_serif1: Hand over the shield!

name: Undine
flavor_text: Water retains no constant shape, instead obeying the form of its vessel. Genbu Mages are no different in their obedience to their leaders. Vassault had no interest in the Sinistrals at first, but he could not ignore the Matriarch's solicitation for help. I have also been led by the Child of Destiny. It was as such 300 years ago, and now is no different.
gacha_text: Your skill... You may be able to help me with a small problem I've been having.
gacha_serif1: Here's 2,000 aurum for your troubles and as an advance. I'm counting on you.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: When you've lived as long as I have, eventually everything becomes boring. Except... the rose. The fascinating beauty of its petals, and the cold, hard rejection of its thorns. I never tire of these opposing qualities.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: The Holy Grail. The vessel that held the blood of the Matriarch. I don't know what sort of power was transferred to the Grail along with that blood. But it is my proud duty to protect the Proof of Good Faith that She Herself demonstrated.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: "Leonid, I appoint you Count of Podorui." The Archfiend's words that day yet ring in my ears. 'Twas a rank given by a mere human. It is a shameful memory despite me being second only to the Sinistrals.
gacha_text: I do hope you will make it there alive.
gacha_serif1: Remarkable job in making it here.

name: Leonid
flavor_text: My memories have faded over the long years. It seems I, too, was human once, but I have no such recollection. There are two humans I do remember though: the Matriarch and the Archfiend.
gacha_text:
Impressive! Here is the
chalice in which once
swirled the blood of
the Matriarch.
