gacha_serif1: I am Count Leonid of Podorui.

name: Professor
flavor_text: Even if I try to hide it, it still shows: I'm a genius. I can't help but make discoveries, each grander than the last. No one can stop me!

name: Professor
flavor_text: Look at my new invention! Actually, just looking won't do it justice. Let's see what happens when you take a hit from it. You won't die, probably! Trust me, I'm a professor!
gacha_text:
Now hold on just a
nanosecond! I'm more
than just my brains
you know.
gacha_serif1: I'm outta here.
gacha_serif2: You're looking at her. That's right. I'm the Professor. The one and only, at the ripe--Er, tender age of thi... twenty.

name: Volcano
flavor_text: The Shucho Arts control Fire Spirits. Aunus, one of the Four Sinistrals, controls fire as well, but he is fire incarnate. His abilities are different from those of a mage. The Shucho Arts emphasize attacking. After all, fire is an intense force. Just like me.

name: Volcano
flavor_text: As thanks for acknowledging my abilities, I'll gladly work with you. The world flourishes on the balance of its spirits. You can't do anything with the Shucho Arts alone. You need other kinds of spells as well.

name: Volcano
flavor_text: There are still so, so many things I don't know about the world. I want to solve these mysteries, and discover the truth. That's why I'm completely involved with absorbing everything I can from Miss Undine right now.
gacha_text: Nice to meet you too, Miss Undine.
gacha_serif1: Air Slash!

name: Volcano
flavor_text: I got her two scoops of ice cream. One red and one blue, her signature colors. But why is she missing? I don't have any spells to keep ice cream from melting!

name: Volcano
flavor_text: The first step is to show a willingness to learn. Let the flame burn in your heart, but learn to control it. The Shucho Arts will respond to two opposing wills. One is the will to burn, the other to control. Okay, you have a go at it now.
gacha_text: Get your spirits fired up! And let's burn!
gacha_serif1: Forgive my overzealous students. I must say, though, you are incredibly talented.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: El Noor. My light, my love. I've always dreamed of the day we'd be reunited. I've waited for so long, with no means to heal your wounds or comfort you. But that all ends today.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: I join now my heart to yours, and engrave upon it the joy of living for tomorrow. I wish to heal your wounds and quench your thirsts. Khalid, you are my light. Now and forever.

name: Fatima
flavor_text: I am allowed to venture out on the night of the festival. I want to see the night market and try exotic stall foods. Most of all, I want to be with you under the lantern lights and look into your eyes. I want to spend this precious time with you.
gacha_text: I told you to stop calling me princess.
gacha_serif1: Princess...
gacha_serif2: But what I admire is your kindness.

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: To become a ray of hope for the people. That is my destiny. The people have but one wish, which is that the Four Sinistrals be forced back into the Abyss. Allow me to raise a flag to rally the troops. We shall vanquish the Sinistrals!
gacha_text: Allow me to raise a flag to rally the troops. We shall vanquish the Sinistrals!
gacha_serif1: I am the... Child of Destiny.

name: Matriarch
flavor_text: I was hesitant to take on the title of Matriarch, but it's my duty as the Child of Destiny to right the wrongs of the Archfiend. I believe now I must fulfill the Matriarch's mission.
gacha_text: It's my duty as the Child of Destiny to right the wrongs of the Archfiend.

name: Paulus
flavor_text: Defeat is what I fear most. It's essential I carefully orchestrate my every move going forward. I must calmly observe the Sinistrals and the Matriarch to ascertain who will win in the end.

name: Paulus
flavor_text: The army of Earthlord Alloces, ruler of Pidona. This is where I must prove myself so that I can be promoted to an officer. Now I must distinguish myself from the rest and fulfill my ambitions. It is time to pull out all the stops!
gacha_text: It is time to pull out all the stops!

name: Paulus
flavor_text: Rebels are gathering in Lance. We should strike them before their numbers grow. I say we provoke and unleash beastmen onto them and we shall see how they fare. If they retaliate, our elite force will crush them.
gacha_text: We shall see how they fare.

name: Vassault
flavor_text: The Sinistrals are uncoordinated. If we strike at each of their individual weaknesses, victory will be ours. Why, then, have we been unable to accomplish this? It is because we are equally unorganized and quarreling.

name: Vassault
flavor_text: The Sinistrals? Not interested. My only wish is to devote my wholehearted attention to the Genbu Arts. The Sinistrals never stood in my way, and I have neither the time nor energy to give them any consideration.
gacha_text: I seek to master Genbu Arts. Leave me be.

name: Vassault
flavor_text: What follows the first victory is key. Some get carried away and try to press on, but we should never do so. We must anticipate the enemy's counterattack and reap the fruits of victory.
gacha_text: We must anticipate the enemy's counterattack and reap the fruits of victory.

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: Until the Matriarch and Dorra bring an end to Byunei, we must do our best to draw the attention of as many enemies as possible and defeat them. Now go wreak havoc upon their ranks, and bring the mightiest of adversaries back to me!

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: I only wanted to settle the frontier. But the Matriarch bestowed upon me the ridiculous title of Marquis of Loanne. I never suspected I'd become a true nobleman. I imagine the one most surprised by this development would be that astronomer.
gacha_text: I do what I must. I will not hesitate to give it my all. That's all there is to it.

name: Ferdinand
flavor_text: Call me a wild boar warrior, a face-first charging fool, whatever you want. I'll be the first one to storm the walls. I'm making things difficult for you as your commander, you say? Well, keep up then!
gacha_text: No, there are still those I must protect. I will not give in that easily!
gacha_serif1: No, there are still those I must protect. I will not give in that easily!

name: Kyrdlund's Mayor
flavor_text: Yes, I am the mayor. What can I do for you? Oh, it's you. Yeees, I remember you. As I recall, you're the one who went to Zweig to help me run an errand, aren't you? No? Then, you must be the one who ran the errand to Podorui. What? Wrong again?

name: Kyrdlund's Mayor
flavor_text: A monster's taken residence near town. We must offer a sacrifice. If only an adventurer would come and defeat it. Well, I suppose that's of no consequence to you cute mice.
gacha_text: I'm sorry, did you say something?
gacha_serif1: I'm the mayor of this town.

name: Asura
flavor_text: There are many humans who seem to mistake me for a dojo master, but that is not the case. Some people have indeed grasped a plethora of skills from fighting me, though that is not why I myself fight!

name: Bunnie
flavor_text: I will never forget you.
gacha_text: I will never forget you.

name: Bunnie
flavor_text: When I awoke I'd been turned into a human! A female one at that! I bet the Professor did this. She promised not to experiment on me anymore! What sort of experiment is Halloween?
gacha_text:
Hehe, now that's a
transformation!
gacha_serif1: Hehe! Now that's a transformation!

name: Bunnie
flavor_text: Do da tssh, do da tssh, bum, ba dum. Do da tssh, do da tssh, bum, ba dum. I've got rhythm in my blood. No need to rush it. Do da tssh, do da tssh, bum, ba dum.

name: Byunei
flavor_text: Having passed through the gate from the dark depths of the Abyss, Byunei, Lord of the Dragons, has descended. My triad will shred your flesh. Trinity Blaster!
gacha_text: Pitiful maggots.

name: Byunei
flavor_text: You can come riding in on Gwayne, Dorra, or any other dragon. But you will be nothing more than a maggot. Crawl on the ground like the maggots you are!

name: Byunei
flavor_text: Plenty of fools tried to challenge me in the Abyss. You shall understand your folly the second I rip you apart. You shall be dead before I finish my move!
gacha_text: Number matters not. You're still nothing but worthless insects.

name: Aunus
flavor_text: 'Tis your fate to die. There is no escaping it. Accept it with grace. In return, I shall grant you a wish. To have your dream come true before you die or to die with your wish unfulfilled: seems like an easy decision to me.

name: Aunus
flavor_text: There was one burdened with the Morastrum, yet resisted their fate with death. But you are different. You do not have the power to resist. So accept your fate! You will suffer otherwise.
gacha_text: Accept your fate!
gacha_serif1: ...'Tis fate.

name: Forneus
flavor_text: Foolish humans... calling their pathetic little boats "warships" and fighting for rule over the ocean. You are merely crawling upon its surface. The true ocean spreads far below.

name: Forneus
flavor_text: I invite you to my Undersea Palace, foolish humans. There are beautiful creatures, wonderful food, and fabulous treasures beyond imagination waiting for you. I, Forneus, Lord of the Sea, shall welcome you.
gacha_text: Taste the power of the Abyss!
gacha_serif1: Taste the power of the Abyss!

name: Blue
flavor_text: I left my hometown to study magic, a journey that continues to this day. With you, I might learn even more about spells. Why don't we travel together?

name: Blue
flavor_text: I have a twin. What was meant for one person was split two ways. Only one of us can become a perfect mage. And that one will be me.
gacha_text:
Who am I?
Blue?
Rouge?

name: Blue
flavor_text: The world's full of red things. I can't stand it! Red clothes and hair, especially. Red things on people are vile. And red-related names? Those are just the worst!

name: Blue
flavor_text: I've been on a long journey to kill Rouge. It all ends here. Once I kill him, I'll become a complete mage again and finally be able to return to the Magic Realm.
gacha_text: Once I kill him, I'll be a complete mage.
gacha_serif1: You can learn more about Arcane and Rune Magic in Devin. Hurry or you won't be able to acquire the spells Rouge has learned!

name: Riki
flavor_text: Margmel's a region of monsters. Riki is a creature called a Lummox. To save Margmel from impending doom, Riki's on a journey to gather rings that grant wishes.

name: Riki
flavor_text: I need to gather all the rings to save Margmel. You'll help me, right? Right? Right right right right right?

name: Riki
flavor_text: This is how Margmel really was. Such a beautiful place with a wonderful aroma and the gentlest of breezes. Yep! Margmel truly was a wonderful world!
gacha_text: Return to your former glory, Margmel!
gacha_serif1: Grandma... So this is the Margmel you told me about.

name: T260G
flavor_text: I'm in the field fighting on Captain Thyme's orders. Where has he gone? I cannot function without orders.

name: T260G
flavor_text: Captain Thyme, I'm afraid I cannot assist you in your search for parts. This arm has a delicate piece that cannot risk being broken. No, Miss Rose, I am not being lazy.
gacha_text: Yes, Captain Thyme.
gacha_serif1: Mobility err-or. Attack err-or.
gacha_serif2: This ungrateful bucket of bolts. I get him working again, and all he can say is "Err-or, err-or."

name: T260G
flavor_text: Mission: Enter Gatalympics and win gold. Probability of victory in Tarzan jump: 99.99%. Probability of sinking when landing on mudflat: 100%. Captain, what should I do?
gacha_text: Mud and salt cause catastrophic failure for mechs.

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: Evil has nowhere to run when THIS superhero is around! A flash of lightning and... Alkaiser Change! Now taste defeat! Al-Phoenix! No one can know my true identity... The transforming hero, Alkaiser, is on the scene!
gacha_text:
I know, Hawke.
We both have a lot
we can't talk about.
gacha_serif1: What's the matter, Hawke?

name: Red
flavor_text: I do have an ace up my sleeve, but I'm not showing you that just yet. I don't need it anyway. Evildoers everywhere, you are going down!

name: Red
flavor_text: Paying your respects at the shrine at the start of a new year is important. For your family's benefit, for Alkaiser's benefit and of course for that cutie in your life! This year, I'm gonna make all my dreams come true!

name: Alkaiser
flavor_text: Dammit. I feel their hits in my bones. Can't see straight... But it is at these times when true heroes rise to the fore. Behold my ultimate attack! Re-Al-Phoenix!
gacha_text: I'll never forgive Black X!
gacha_serif1: Re-Al-Phoenix

name: Emelia
flavor_text: My hopes, my dreams, my ideals, my fiance... You took everything from me. I will never forgive you! Now, show yourself, so I can send you to hell where you belong!
gacha_text: Unforgivable...!
gacha_serif1: Joker...

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Just a regular battle outfit this time. My usual role is supporting Annie, Lyza, or Roufas with Suppressing Fire. I'm not a Gladius cosplayer or anything weird like that.
gacha_text: I won't forget you.
gacha_serif1: What a nice view... Such clear skies... I feel like I could forget all about Joker...

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Those legendary soldiers who could make it back safely from a battlefield or mission, no matter how difficult, without breaking a sweat... I am like them now. By sharpening my senses and my mind, I can keep my cool at all times when on a mission.
gacha_text: I seem to be a pretty good shot.
gacha_serif1: Oh, so this is a pistol! I've never shot one before!

name: Asellus
flavor_text: I always wondered who I really was. Was I human? Mystic? Neither? But I had no need to wonder. I am Asellus. And that's all I need to know.
gacha_serif1: And so I continue to live with this destiny. That's all I wanted to say.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: To be honest with you, I was perplexed as to why I had to receive chocolates. But I couldn't very well let your sincerity go unanswered, could I? So, please help yourself to one of these.
gacha_text:
This world is so wonderful...
and so free...
gacha_serif1: Have you seen Princess White Rose?

name: Asellus
flavor_text: This is an important ritual to free an imprisoned soul. And it's the only way. Compose yourself, Asellus. Clear your mind and just fight. You're a mystic, you can do this.
gacha_text:
I've learned that it's alright
to like myself just the way
I am.
gacha_serif1: And so I continue to live with this destiny. That's all I wanted to say.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: Does the festival get my blue mystic blood pumping, or my red human blood? Either way, when I march through town with those enormous hikiyama festival floats, all my worries fade.
gacha_text:
Enya, enya!
Yoisa, yoisa!

name: Asellus
flavor_text: What color is your blood? If it's red, can I have some? Wait! I was doing my vampire lines. I don't REALLY want red blood. I swear.

name: Lute
flavor_text: It's a crazy world we're livin' in. And me worryin' wouldn't do a thing. Sometimes you just gotta wait these things out, you know? Let's just take it easy.
gacha_text: Yo, cutie, how you doin'?
gacha_serif1: Well, I'll be going now.

name: Lute
flavor_text: Doo doo doo, dee dee dee, da da da, la la la, fee fee feee, day da day da daaa, la dee doo da day...

name: Fuse
flavor_text: IRPO brings in tons of agents from various regions, so we are a motley crew. But there can only be one Number 1. Do you know who that is? That's right, the very man standing before you now!
gacha_text: Leave it to me.
gacha_serif1: I'm going to rip away Campbell's facade.

name: Ren
flavor_text: Emelia, you are my everything. Nothing in this region is more precious to me. I'll even resign as an IRPO officer if you want. I have eyes only for you, and I want you to look only at me.

name: Ren
flavor_text: Isn't he just great? Why, you say? Well, he's a flop with the ladies. Probably because he goes over the top on everything. He's also a chatterbox, which girls hate. I probably shouldn't tell him about Emelia.
gacha_text: Probably because he goes over the top on everything.
gacha_serif1: When's the next time you can take a vacation?
gacha_serif2: I don't think I'll be getting a vacation.

name: Silence
flavor_text:
Silence's notes:
I might have things to say, but I can guess the person's reply and the result of the conversation. And since that's how it is, there's no need to say anything. Excessive talking is not a virtue.

name: Doll
flavor_text: What's my relationship with Fuse? What do you mean by that? I am a member of the IRPO and so is Fuse. That's it. Fuse is talented, but he doesn't know how to plan ahead. What's important is to get the desired results with the least amount of input and to have a Plan B.
gacha_text: Name's Doll. I'm an IRPO officer.
gacha_serif1: Now's your only chance to laugh.

name: Rabbit
flavor_text: I don't know much about all the different types of rabbits, so I don't know if I actually look like a rabbit or not. In any case, my code name is just used for identification purposes, so it doesn't matter what I'm called. I do quite like this name, though.

name: Cotton
flavor_text: Mew mew? Mew mew chirp chirp! Mew mew mew, chirp chirp. Chiiiirp meeeew. Mew mew mew!
gacha_text: Chirp chirp chirp!
gacha_serif1: Hey, Cotton!

name: Roufas
flavor_text: What it means to be top brass is that you don't have to get your hands dirty to get things done. Don't assume that I'll save you when you get into trouble. If you understand that, then get to work.
gacha_text: We are the secret organization Gladius.
gacha_serif1: There must be an organization to do all the things IRPO can't.

name: Annie
flavor_text: You must really have a death wish if you're starting a fight with me. Well, people are into all sorts of things, so I'll indulge you. Prepare to get hurt.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Hey, what's gonna happen? Is it gonna be dangerous? Good! Life's no fun without a little danger.
gacha_text:
From here on out
you're a volunteer.
gacha_serif1: Hey, keep your distance!

name: Annie
flavor_text: I'm Annie, captain of the Gladius Bandwagon. Launching headfirst into danger? That's what I do. But only because I know Lyza, Roufas, and Emelia have my back.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Our work is mostly gathering intel. But with the exception of assassinations, we do everything. We do our best to abide by the law, but when things get dicey, the job comes first. We are not heroes by any stretch of the imagination, but neither are we villains.
gacha_text: Doing things the right way means nothing if you're dead.
gacha_serif1: Are you also interested in matters concerning the Cube?
gacha_serif2: Not really. I don't really care all that much.

name: Annie
flavor_text: Your sniper rifle, with its long range and accuracy, has been set up in a place with no blind spots. And you, the person behind the scope, never miss a shot. You are the epitome of perfection. But, unfortunately for you, I've already gotten through your defenses!
gacha_text: Don't just call out to me like that. Things could get bloody.
gacha_serif1: I'm Annie. This has happened 3, 4, 5... or maybe 6 times already.

name: Lyza
flavor_text: Whatever you need, I can help. Legal, illegal... what sort of services do you require? I promise you we won't let you down.

name: Lyza
flavor_text: You let your guard down because I don't use weapons. But these fists and feet are all the weapons I need. Care for more?

name: Lyza
flavor_text: Perhaps you're thinking, "Someone would actually arrange a meet up in a dark alley like this?" Even if I am waiting for someone, it's not you. Besides, with your ugly mug, I don't think there'd be anyone willing to wait for you.
gacha_text: Perhaps you're thinking, "Someone would actually arrange a meet up in a dark alley like this?"
gacha_serif1: Ok, I'll try that. You're so kind.
gacha_serif2: But people often say I'm a cold-hearted woman.

name: M Black
flavor_text: I may be one of the top brass in Black X, but I am alone. I care not for their schemes or who is the strongest. I'm simply waiting to fight that man. Solitude is ideal.
gacha_text: I request a duel.
gacha_serif1: You destroyed my facility. Remarkable.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: I am Rouge. I'm on the trail of a mage called Blue. What will I do when I find him, you ask? Defeat him. That's all there is to it.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: I'm not strong enough yet. Without more power, I cannot face my other half. Hey you, do you know of a place where I can acquire power?

name: Rouge
flavor_text: I may look like a man, but in fact I'm only half of one. I am indeed half a person. And when I obtain my other half, that day will be the true day of my birth.
gacha_text:
I'm traveling the world in order
to study magic.
gacha_serif1: I am the Realm sorcerer, Rouge. I travel the world to master skills and spells.

name: Rouge
flavor_text: My entire life has led to this day. I'd nearly given up, but I recalled that figure looming over me and I was able to rise again. Blue, I'll thank you for that... Once I kill you.
gacha_text: My entire life has led to this day.
gacha_serif1: I can't return to the Realm. Not yet. This is where we go our separate ways.

name: Gen
flavor_text: Hey. Name's Gen. Take a seat. Go on. Take a load off. Don't worry, everything works out in the end.

name: Gen
flavor_text: I spent all my time in Wakatu learning how to use a sword. In the end, I could wield it like it was an extension of my body. But none of my training made any difference against Trinity's weapons, and Wakatu was destroyed.

name: Gen
flavor_text: I'm here to show you clowns a real warrior. Is Asura in charge around here? Or is it that lobster? Not important, now that I'm here. Let's start things off by you getting me a drink.
gacha_text: Close your eyes. Use your ears.
gacha_serif1: This is the Chamber of the Bladewraith.

name: Mei-ling
flavor_text: When I say rings, I don't mean the engagement kind. There are some powerful rings in this world. I don't know who made them, but I know they're out there.

name: Mei-ling
flavor_text: A bright moon lights up the night, yet I'm alone. A special time to spend with someone at your side. I feel ever the more lonely. What about you? Are you alone? Perhaps this is the cost of ambition.
gacha_text: What a coincidence. I'm looking for rings, too. Where have you come from?
gacha_serif1: You sure know a lot about the rings.
gacha_serif2: It's because I'm currently studying the rings. Riki, what's up with that ring?

name: Fei-on
flavor_text: I have so much more training to undergo. Yet, it is undeniable that real battle is a superior form of training, so come at me, and do not stop. My training has only just begun.
gacha_text: I keep my hair like this for my training.
gacha_serif1: I was eaten by Tanzer, that's why...
gacha_serif2: You never change... Making me wait because you have to train.

name: Princess Rei
flavor_text: Even Orlouge will find it hard to follow me to this world. His persistence is vexing. Does he not realize the chased will run? Lord of Temptation? An ill-fitting name.

name: Princess Rei
flavor_text: Did you think this is some sort of game? With power comes sacrifice, but a Mystic's power knows no bounds. That is why humans should not use it lightly.
gacha_text: What business do you have with me?
gacha_serif1: It's sold out.

name: Princess Lion
flavor_text: We both fight for the one we love. Neither victory nor defeat will make us waver in our undying devotion to the wonders of love. Is there anything more important than this to those who were born to love? Now, let us settle this with a fight!
gacha_text: I shall defeat you with all that I am!
gacha_serif1: I'm only after one person, and it's not you.
gacha_serif2: The time for words is over. Let's settle this with a fight.

name: Princess Lion
flavor_text: My heart yearns for a love it cannot come close to fulfilling. The more I pursue my dreams, the further out of reach it becomes. It is precisely because I cannot convey my feelings that they are all the more precious. Hanging on to these emotions to the very end satisfies both my mind and my body.
gacha_text: The only one who has yet to succumb to this sword is Lord Orlouge.
gacha_serif1: I am your opponent!
gacha_serif2: Hmph! The only one to have never succumbed to the might of my sword is Lord Orlouge himself!

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: Lord Orlouge truly loved me like he loved his white roses. He gave me their name, and made me his 46th concubine. I would never betray him.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: Don't tell me you couldn't eat them all because they're too sweet. I want you to finish them, finish all of them.
gacha_text:
You look wonderful in it,
though! So charming
and magical!
gacha_serif1: You look wonderful in it, though! So charming and magical!

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I am White Rose. I surely once had another name, but I forgot it. I can be nothing but White Rose. This name represents all that I am. That is what becoming a concubine entails.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I wish to be true to my name as the noble white rose. Still, I love red and orange roses, too. Had I been Lord Orlouge's 16th concubine, I'd have been Princess Rainbow Rose.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: Lord Orlouge asked me to educate Lady Asellus. We will fail unless we work together. I want to stay true to my feelings.
gacha_text: I will teach you everything about Mystics, about myself, and about Lord Orlouge.
gacha_serif1: Who... who are you?
gacha_serif2: Lady Asellus, I hope all is well.

name: Mesarthim
flavor_text: I want to leave the lake and travel the world, but I worry whether a Water Mystic can live away from it. After all, I don't have the strength of those nobles.
gacha_text: The scent of a noble Mystic... But how? She's human.
gacha_serif1: Ask of me what you will. I am your servant.
gacha_serif2: No, you are not my servant.

name: Mesarthim
flavor_text: I know there are good humans as there are also a great deal of evil Mystics. But the stench of humans is repulsive. My mind tries to resist, but my nose rejects it.
gacha_text: I can't stand the stench of humans. I find myself choking on it...
gacha_serif1: I can smell the lake!

name: Thunder
flavor_text: Bad guys, huh?! Leave it to me, Big Bro! Yeah, I'm not good for much, except when it comes to going on a rampage! You just stand back and give me some music to get me goin'.

name: Red Turnip
flavor_text: Just Red Turnip is fine. Call me Miss Red Turnip, or whatever, and I'm bound to blush as red as a-- wait, my whole body is normally red! Bwa ha ha!

name: Engineer Car
flavor_text: Machines that fight on the front line are important, but they must be serviced and maintained. The Engineer Car is an all-purpose mech that can perform repairs under the harshest battlefield conditions.

name: Orlouge
flavor_text: Everyone desires to yield to an almighty being. Their lives are easier without the heavy burden that is choice. Give your hearts to me. Don't be bound by liberty. A life of joy is its own reward.

name: Orlouge
flavor_text: Mystic hierarchy is absolute. It is impossible for the low to defy the high. Mystics are above other races. Our actions are not beholden to such notions as the law of the land.
gacha_text: I shall build a nation of Mystics in this world. Yes, a fine idea, I must say.
gacha_serif1: The blue blood of a Mystic and the red blood of a human are both inside your body.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: The power of steel is the power of human will. Let steel, not magic, be the source of your power. When you do, your path will open up before you.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: Raise the troops' morale? Damn you, Kelvin... You talk like it's so easy. Why would the words of a failure like me boost their spirits? I'll tell them this and it'll be all they should need: Onward, into battle!
gacha_text:
Aaahh...
For some reason, I feel my heart lifting. It's been a
while since I've felt this way.
gacha_serif1: Motherrrr... !

name: Gustave
flavor_text: I conquered the entire Eastern Continent, and the city of Hahn Nova is being rebuilt. It may become the greatest city in the world. But what now? Who wants a reject for a ruler?

name: Gustave
flavor_text: Whoever wins this battle wins the throne. I've no interest in the throne, but for the sake of my friends who've stuck by me, I will win. And above all, I must win for Mother.
gacha_text:
I just want to see
what I am capable of.

name: Gustave
flavor_text: To think so many people are unskilled in magic. The downtrodden. Those with nothing to lose. They are led by me, a man with no Anima. I should be the first to fall, since no one would mourn my death.
gacha_text: No one's asking you to do it. I'll take care of it myself.
gacha_serif1: Tell every commander that we aren't taking any prisoners.

name: Wil
flavor_text: I'm Wil. I came here looking for my first job as a digger. What do you say? Shall we form a party? The more in our ranks, the greater the peace of mind.
gacha_text: It must be somewhere on this ship. I'm gonna sink the Egg to the bottom of the sea!
gacha_serif1: Of course.
gacha_serif2: Understood.

name: Wil
flavor_text: I'm a digger, so to return the favor, I give Quells instead of chocolates. This is a special kind of Quell that'll warm your heart.

name: Wil
flavor_text: This isn't alcohol. Nothing beats this after a soak. It replenishes the Anima within. Anima permeate every part of us. And this? Let's just say it tastes even better at my age. Ho ho ho!

name: Wil
flavor_text: The day for presents has come! I want all the children to be happy tomorrow morning. I've got a lot of presents to deliver. Ones that a rich person would covet.
gacha_text: Merry Christmas! Ho ho ho!
gacha_serif1: Merry Christmas! Ho ho ho!

name: Rich
flavor_text: I'm Rich... in name only, I'm afraid, seeing as I'm flat broke. No matter how many Quells I dig up, I never seem to have any money. Why is that?

name: Rich
flavor_text: I'll protect my family. I won't let something like the Egg threaten them.

name: Rich
flavor_text: Why're you looking at me like that? It's not like I sold any presents. I just got an advance on my Santa salary, so I'm filling up the tank before takeoff. Share a toast on this holy night?
gacha_text: I'm Rich Knights. How about we make a rainbow appear over this Holy Night winter wonderland?
gacha_serif1: I'm always getting the cold shoulder, but tonight is different... What do I do?

name: Ginny
flavor_text: Anima reside in all things in the world. Both living creatures, as well as inanimate objects. The forest is filled with Anima. Anima of the forest, lend me your power!

name: Ginny
flavor_text: I myself am the youngest in a proud line of Knights diggers. I know all too well how dangerous it is to get one's hands on Quells. Are you ready? Let's go.
gacha_text:
Dad... Mom... Grandpa...
Everyone... Don't let the Egg
beat you!

name: Ginny
flavor_text: Ha-haaa, I'm not cold at all, even if I'm dressed like this. I have Quells in my pocket that keep me warm. All right! Time to give out some presents!
gacha_text:
What a great idea! Everyone'll
be so happy.

name: Ginny
flavor_text: This relaxes me head to toes. It makes me feel whole. This Peg toy is cute, don't you think? Sorry for hitting you earlier. Seems the old folks are having a soak now, so I'll wait.
gacha_text: Come here and we'll go in together.
gacha_serif1: Over here, Claudia! Come on in!

name: Ginny
flavor_text: The Egg is a long-time enemy of my grandfather. It attracts vile Anima. I will not lose to such Anima. I am scared, though. Father, give me strength!
gacha_text: Fighting for someone is such a great feeling.
gacha_serif1: I feel so at peace for some reason. Such a mysterious feeling...

name: Flynn
flavor_text: Across the sea... The land where you were born is there, Sir Gus. I know it's impossible, but how I would love to see it. I bet going there would make me a whole new person.

name: Flynn
flavor_text: There are akebia here, too. We share a lot of memories with those, don't we, Sir Gus? You probably don't need akebia now that you can eat whatever you want, but how about a bite?

name: Flynn
flavor_text: However scary a monster is, just avoid it. Stop, move forward, change direction, then slip right by it before you're even within range of its attacks. No matter how weak you are, or even if you can't use magic, you can't lose if you just don't fight.
gacha_text: Would it be all right if I wait here?
gacha_serif1: Sir Gus, I'm scared. There are monsters here, right?

name: Johan
flavor_text: Adapt your Anima to your surroundings. Doing so will remove all indications of your presence. You can move all you like, even stand right in front of your adversaries, and they will have no idea that you're there.

name: Johan
flavor_text: Soon the scorpion will crawl up to the back of my neck. Its venom will spread through my veins, and I will die. I am fine with this. After all, it was I who chose to live a life of freedom.

name: Johan
flavor_text: I'll show you what my Assassin Arts are all about! Until the day the Scorpions come for me!

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I may be a novice, but I am a sentry too. I have what it takes. I only lack experience. Oh, my name is Cordelia. Nice to meet you.
gacha_text:
I might not look like much,
but I have confidence in
my abilities. I only lack
experience.
gacha_serif1: I'm Cordelia. We sentries guard diggers like you. Nice to meet you, Wil.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: Have some Quells! ...I wish I could say that, but for today, you'll have to settle for some homemade chocolates. I really like you, so... I want you to have these.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I'm using a special spell to make kitty here more comfy. It really works, huh? Doesn't help for travels on the road, but it's my signature move. Does it work on people too? I don't know. I've never tried it.

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: Each of these presents will bring a smile to a child's face somewhere. I am enveloped in happiness right now with joy in the palm of my hands. This deed warms my heart.
gacha_text: At this rate, we won't be able to deliver all the presents before the night is up.
gacha_serif1: How're things over there, Labelle?

name: Cordelia
flavor_text: I don't know enough about this world. I must learn more to fight more effectively. And this is the perfect spot to do so. I'd also like to learn more about... you.
gacha_text: I must learn more to fight more effectively.

name: Labelle
flavor_text: The woods are full of Anima. Those who don't care for the woods, don't care for Anima. You value Anima, don't you? I wonder if you would treat my Anima with the same care...
gacha_text: Let's go then.
gacha_serif1: You do?!
gacha_serif2: I know another way there.

name: Labelle
flavor_text: This night gives my heart warmth. When you think of another's Anima, your own Anima warms up. Strange, isn't it? That's why I welcome the downhearted to my party. Please, step right in.
gacha_text: Rrrgh! Now where did Wil and Rich get off to?!
gacha_serif1: We'll just have to do what we can. It's now a race to finish before sunrise.

name: Roberto
flavor_text: Ginny fights valiantly for her family. And I am the cool hero who protects her. I'm like the protagonist of an adventure novel. How can you not call this fate?
gacha_text: Ugh! Guess I have to fight!
gacha_serif1: We will be victorious. This thing...

name: Primiera
flavor_text: A nobleman's daughter is just a tool in his fight for power. I left because I didn't want that fate for myself. Even as I face evil Anima, my heart is filled with joy. This is where I'll spend my days.
gacha_text: Stepmother, father, give me power!
gacha_serif1: Such an overwhelming Anima! It feels like it's piercing my body...

name: Primiera
flavor_text: I feel a bit uneasy without my armor. But what's this sense of freedom? It feels like I've shed armor from not just my body, but my heart as well. I feel so light, like I have wings.

name: Gustaf
flavor_text: Firebrand, the royal symbol of Finney, and the great steel sword forged by Marquis Gustave himself. With these two legendary swords, the Egg's ambitions will be cut down! Hopefully I can achieve that...
gacha_text: Oh Firebrand, can I put my faith in you?
gacha_serif1: The Firebrand... It's resonating with the Egg!

name: Laura
flavor_text: Don't overextend yourself. Leave this area to me. After all, I could go on a rampage and no one's gonna say anything.

name: Laura
flavor_text: You haven't heard of the Sea Wolf? Must be your first time on the waves. Well, you have two choices. Either I take whatever treasure's on you, and you go back home and remember my name, or... I take your life and feed you to the fishes.

name: Laura
flavor_text: One after another, you just don't quit. Why don't you give up already? As long as I'm around, you won't get any closer. If you still want to go at it, then fine, I'll humor you.
gacha_text: Come any closer and you WILL get hurt!
gacha_serif1: What about it?!
gacha_serif2: You're Prince Henri of Escata, right?

name: Judie
flavor_text: Listen to this! So today, Mommy got mad at Roy again because he wouldn't eat his dinner. Then Marie got called next door. So... I'll make your dinner for you myself -- with magic!
gacha_text: It's OK. Just leave it to me!
gacha_serif1: Sure! You going out?
gacha_serif2: Judie, could you watch the shop?

name: Armic
flavor_text: I dunno which way to go. The wind's blowing from that direction, so maybe I should head that way. Why do I hafta go on this stupid journey? Won't someone tell me?
gacha_text: Aaah... I just want to go home.
gacha_serif1: Oh, is it an alphabet?

name: Henri
flavor_text: As King of Escata, I am ready to rebuild my nation. My people will surely look up to me as an example, so I carry that burden as well. I can do these things because of what Laura has taught me.

name: Henri
flavor_text: My father and mother are no longer in this world. All those dear people of Escata perished in the chaos of that night. I'll never see any of them again.

name: Silver Emperor
flavor_text: This world must also battle darkness? My experience here should help in our own fight, but I don't hear the voices of Cat and Emerald. Things seem different. All I can do is keep moving forward.

name: Silver Emperor
flavor_text: Selma, I entrust this world's future to you. Should I lose my life... No, when I lose my life, I can bequeath my wishes upon you. It will be a great burden, but a worthwhile one. I love you.
gacha_text: Seeing her face, my resolve almost wavered.
gacha_serif1: ...Let me know when you're ready to depart.

name: Selma
flavor_text: Hmm... Yeah, sure. Someday, if I meet the right person. Someone kind and gentle, but noble-minded, like my father.

name: Selma
flavor_text: My father is fighting somewhere out there in the world. That thought gives me the strength to go on!
gacha_text:
No need for that tone.
What in the world
are you doing?
gacha_serif1: I don't care how dangerous it is! That just makes it all the better for sword training!

name: Selma
flavor_text: There's always someone by me, supporting me. I'm grateful, but sometimes I just wanna be alone. I wanna go somewhere all alone, strip naked and be free! No one can see the real me.
gacha_text:
This will let me
breathe underwater, right?
gacha_serif1: It isn't moving, so it's not a fish. There's... something beneath the waves.

name: Selma
flavor_text: You are the customer, Father. I'm the shop owner. Hello, can I take your order? Oh, we don't serve alcohol. Would tea be okay? Here you go. Have some cake, too! It's delicious.
gacha_text: I'm lonely, but I'll be okay.
gacha_serif1: My apologies. I have acted so childish in front of you all...

name: Urpina
flavor_text: Today, Elysed is coming to visit. If I'm not better behaved than usual, I'll make a fool of myself in front of her. But I think I can squeeze in some monster exterminating before she arrives.

name: Urpina
flavor_text: Two swords is the fighting style of my family, the House of Julanius. Even if I cannot handle them as well as my father or brother, it is a skill I too must learn. Now come, Mondo. Fight me.
gacha_text:
Brother... I did it. Your little
sister did it.
gacha_serif1: Brother... I'll kill... No way! I can't do it!

name: Urpina
flavor_text: What led me here? A Deity, or a Demonic Overlord? If this is fate, all I can do is fight for the honor of House Julanius! I'll face it head on, fearless, with all my might!
gacha_text:
For the honor of
House Julanius!

name: Urpina
flavor_text: I've finally mastered the dual wielding technique of House Julanius. Brother's still leagues beyond me, but I'd like to present the technique to everyone who supported me!
gacha_text: Urpina Finish!
gacha_serif1: Mother wielded a fearsome blade at Father's side, and I shall do no less for the House of Julanius!

name: Leonard
flavor_text: Hey, are we doing this or not? How about this: whoever wins is right.

name: Leonard
flavor_text: This is our traditional victory pose. After fighting with all our might, we squat down to take a break. Let me do what I want.
gacha_text: You all just keep coming, don't you?
gacha_serif1: All right, that oughta do it for the harvest. I finished the fastest again this year for sure.

name: Taria
flavor_text: I had fun with my witchcraft when I was young. I thought I could do anything, but that was not so. No magic can change your heart. Perhaps I was destined to use this power once more.
gacha_text: Don't expect too much from me. I'm but a humble potter.
gacha_serif1: Kahn, you came. I must set out again.

name: Taria
flavor_text: Long ago, a potter far from home discovered how to calm his soul by grinding stone to powder, then forming and firing it to make porcelain. He could get lost in his work and forget all his worries. I know this feeling, for I too have things I wish to forget.
gacha_text: Porcelain making is big in this town.

name: Balmaint
flavor_text: This axe is for lopping off heads in one fell swoop. It's different from a battle axe, which is for live combat. Both are axes, but their shapes and purposes are very different.
gacha_text:
I have to accept
what he said.
gacha_serif1: Any last words?

name: Balmaint
flavor_text: Only those allowed by Imperial Law could carry out sentences. I was one of those people, but that doesn't make me special. I'm just an average guy.

name: Elisabeth
flavor_text: I know looking for Ei-Hanum is important, but we might as well explore while we're at it. You know, like go sight-seeing, grab a meal... It sure is great to escape my old man's watchful eye!

name: Elisabeth
flavor_text: I'm sure you realize you did something wrong. But you're sorely mistaken if you think it'll all be fine with an apology. You have to pay for what you did. So, which will it be? Left or right hand?
gacha_text: They must face the music. I won't turn a blind eye.
gacha_serif1: "Suit yourself"? What's that supposed to mean! You don't get to tell me that! Got it?! Let's get going already!

name: Sasha
flavor_text: Who I am matters not. This world's spiritual energy is in disarray. We must find out why and restore balance. I'd love to have your help. You won't say no, will you?
gacha_text: Who I am matters not.
gacha_serif1: Who I am matters not. As upset as the flow of spiritual energy is here, it'd be awful if one were to now use the Firebringer shards.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Prakity Prakian. That was the circus Liz and I were in. Who would've thought the ringmaster would...

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Father... I know somehow the Shucho Arts will reveal the truth to me. I have inherited them from you. I'm still learning how to use them, but I am up to the task, Father.
gacha_text: Not just my father, but my mother, too. I feel they're watching over Liz and me now.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Out of desperation, I almost went down a bad path. But Liz was there to keep me on the straight and narrow. Somehow, just barely... I made it through alive.
gacha_text: Happy New Year everyone. Please lend me your strength this year, too.
gacha_serif1: Actually, this is my first time celebrating the New Year like this, so I'm not sure what to do.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: There's a shark warning?! I can't let Liz go into the water! Here, this flamingo will be your bait. Hang on tight! And don't get the wrong idea, of course I can swim without it!

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: When Jo was born, I was so happy. I thought I would be her father. That's why I was against hiding her in Mazewood. I am the only one who can protect Jo. I cannot leave her protection to someone else.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: I inherited the Shucho Arts from my father. But I need to learn even stronger Shucho magic. I must become stronger. If I don't, I won't be able to protect my family and Jo.
gacha_text: If I don't, I won't be able to protect my family and Jo.
gacha_serif1: Jo was still a baby. She doesn't remember us at all.

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: My brother became a Grave Knight to save me. There must be something I can do, too!

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: I was trapped in that cave forever. This vacation is almost surreal. And I looove ice cream. Where did Polka go, by the way?
gacha_text:
Polka's life depends
on this... floatie.
Hee hee.
gacha_serif1: I think it suits you. Try it on.

name: Robingirl
flavor_text: What a perfect costume. Now no one, especially my brother, will know who I am. I've been dying to try this -- I'm now the Masked Crusader Robin! Hope some evildoers show up soon.

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: The Genbu Arts control water. I have a natural gift for magic thanks to my parentage. Their power protects me. But from now on, it's my turn to use my power to protect others.
gacha_text: The only way to make it through this is to fight. I'm not running away.
gacha_serif1: I saw him, just for a brief moment. He's headed for the Arch Witch. I have to hurry!

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: When I held Jo to my chest after she was born, I couldn't stop crying. I was so thankful. I swore to become stronger for you. I had to give you up to the care of others to continue my search for more strength.

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Water has no form and thus can take any form. That is the essence of Genbu Arts. But now, my mind and heart are dedicated to protecting Jo. I should put my all into the Genbu Arts and set my soul free. However, it's... so difficult. Jo, you are all I can think about.
gacha_text: I want to hug Jo with all my might.
gacha_serif1: Have you already forgotten how much trouble your recklessness has caused?

name: Shen Du
flavor_text: Since long ago, we astronomers of Dae have interacted with the Johannes sect in the town of Lance. They may know something about Master Dahao's whereabouts.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: The lost memories belonging to the heroes from 300 years ago... The truth behind them may be hidden in the shrines scattered around the world.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: We live under one roof, through joy and sorrow. The lobster clan values married life as well.

name: Valdor
flavor_text: Look at the spiral! You are getting sleepy, sleeeepy... What? No! I'm not trying to hypnotize you. This spiral has the power to unearth the truth. The truth!
gacha_text: Look at the spiral!
gacha_serif1: Having trouble sleeping, Polka?

name: Valdor
flavor_text: Listen up. Results are the product of ability and time. That is to say, if two people have the same ability, the one who puts in more time will achieve superior results. So, how do you surpass someone better than you? Only training will do, of course!
gacha_text: Time is a limited resource. Do not waste it.
gacha_serif1: Be sure to enhance your fighters.

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: That Polka... At the beginning, I thought he was a useless little brat. Goes to show what some instruction from yours truly can do, huh?

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: You think I'm satisfied with this small fry?! This ain't a catch. It's bait! Keep those peepers peeled. I'm gonna reel me in a massive monster!

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: I... I wasn't always alone. There were others... many, many others like me!

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: Faeries are good at music. Everyone knows that. The bagpipes can be tricky, but I'll show ya how it's done. All right, let's go! Whoa, this thing is loud! You could wake the dead.
gacha_text: I command thee to listen to my performance!
gacha_serif1: Don't try to smooth-talk me. You're not going to win me over like that.

name: Faerie (Brownie)
flavor_text: Y'know, it feels like I've been given the cold shoulder lately. You see anyone else who can move like me? Those Otherworld Warriors are a bunch of good-for-nothings! Leave everything to me!
gacha_text: Those Otherworld Warriors are a bunch of good-for-nothings!
gacha_serif1: Why I oughta! Get back here you stinkin' faerie!

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: It is a Gessian legend. When this flame goes out, the sun itself shall go out.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: The true Khamsin is obtained by relinquishing what you hold dearest. That means the Khamsin has become more important to me than anything else. I have no regrets... Absolutely none!
gacha_text: I... chose the Khamsin.
gacha_serif1:
Art thou...
...Khamsin's successor?

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: I have a duty to lead the people of Gessiah. I cannot follow every word of Zenon's. If protecting Polka's family goes against the safety of my people, I will have to make a tough decision.

name: Madeleine
flavor_text: Khamsin, what do you wish of me? To expand the Naj Kingdom and start wars with neighboring kingdoms? To lead the people in living poor, yet peaceful lives? Or for me to be at the whim of the Child of Destiny? Tell me what it is exactly you want!
gacha_text: Khamsin, what do you wish of me?
gacha_serif1: Polka, Liz, Tatyana. I'm glad you came.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: Emperor Fegan of Messina hopes to destroy the Marquisate of Loanne by ordering Zenon to be put to death. However, the emperor's power has been undercut by a surge of people who oppose destroying post-Matriarchal Loanne.

name: Zenon
flavor_text: I've spent the 15 years since leaving the manor at Loanne alone in nature. The cries of the animals and the whispers of the wind point to every fabric that makes up this world. My path forward has been made clear to me.
gacha_text: My path forward has been made clear to me.

name: Jo
flavor_text: I don't know what happened in the past, but if you really cared about me, you wouldn't have kept me away, Mother.

name: Jo
flavor_text: Uncle and Auntie used to be enemies in their old world. I'm not really sure if they get along now or not, but I can tell they need each other.
gacha_text: If you try to lose on purpose, I'll be furious.
gacha_serif1: My name is Josephine Lynn Wood, but everyone calls me Jo.

name: Jo
flavor_text: Even in costume, I have to be the strongest. So, I made a Genny costume with just a little help from others. I'll battle everyone in this. Man, this is gonna be fun!

name: Genryu
flavor_text: Water can take many forms. It can turn into a shield, like a mirror that reflects the enemy's attacks. The Mirror Shield... Just try and take it from me.

name: Genryu
flavor_text: I'm a dragon with the powers of both fire and water. Why was such a being brought into existence? Who knows, but the fact is that I do exist. She accepted me and everything I was born as. She never rejected me. I like her.
gacha_text: Are dragons rare?
gacha_serif1: Who goes there?

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: I don't want you to be especially wealthy or famous. I just want you to be special to someone.

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: Polka and Liz... Keep your eye on those two. They are an important part of this. Why are they important? Because they are chess pieces. Important chess pieces.
gacha_text: Oh Lil' Polka. How you've grown in such a short time.
gacha_serif1: I was born to be a killer.

name: Barthelemy
flavor_text: Clowns are here for the entertainment of others. But I'm different. I'm a clown for my own enjoyment. Everything is a show for my sake. And now, the curtain opens!
gacha_text: And now, the curtain opens!
gacha_serif1: Lil' Polka. How does it feel to be under the limelight once again?

name: Evelyn
flavor_text: I did not show myself during the disaster 600 years ago, nor did I leave my cave during the one 300 years ago. I did not sense the Archfiend's presence then.

name: Golden Baum
flavor_text: Mutated Golden Baum specimen, found in a Grave. Did the mutation come about from distortions in space and time that occur in Graves? Or did it travel here from a different dimension? We may never know...

name: Golden Baum
flavor_text: When I get into water, I start to spread out. It feels greeeat. Water is flowing through me, making me swell and expand. Water's the best!
gacha_text: Water is flowing through me, making me swell and expand. Water's the best!
gacha_serif1: What is this?! It's so fun!

name: Minstrel
flavor_text: It is not the poems of gods but rather the words of the common people that ought to be sung in this land. Words flock to a soul that is at the mercy of an undeniable fate. Beautiful or foul, only truth can rouse the heart.
gacha_text: Will you listen to this tale?
gacha_serif1:
-Yes.
-No.
gacha_serif2: Shall I sing thee a story?

name: Albert
flavor_text: The hardest part about being left-handed is the fact that most weapons and armor are made for right-handed individuals. You right-handers probably won't understand the difference.

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: The Imperial Throne has been passed on for generations. It contains all the aspirations of past emperors. This is what it means to sit on the throne. Should I fail, all those aspirations come to naught. This heavy burden will give me strength.
gacha_text:
Stop calling me Your Majesty. I
am the emperor no more.

name: Asellus
flavor_text: I always wondered who I really was. Was I human? Mystic? Neither? But I had no need to wonder. I am Asellus. And that's all I need to know.
gacha_text:
I'm me. I like me. I've realized
that's good enough for me.

name: Polka Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Flavor text TBD

name: Liz Lynn Wood
flavor_text: Flavor text TBD

name: Professor
flavor_text: Flavor text TBD

name: Leon
flavor_text:
Now, here's to everyone's health. Cheers!
Here's to a bountiful harvest. Cheers!
And, here's to victory tomorrow. Cheers!
gacha_text: Drink up!
gacha_serif1: The return of the Seven Heroes won't bring about peace any time soon. Battles will ensue.

name: Final Emperor
flavor_text: The threat of the Seven Heroes is no more. My duty and those of the generations of emperors before me have come to an end. The time has come to free ourselves from Emperor Leon's long-standing wishes. We dedicate this evening's banquet to all the emperors who led us here. Let us enjoy one last moment together.
gacha_text: Everything will end. That's something to rejoice about.

name: Final Empress
flavor_text: I have put an end to the ambitions of the Seven Heroes for the good of the people of the Varennes Empire. My duty to carry on the wishes of the emperors is at an end. I wish now for a new purpose.
gacha_text: I am no longer the empress.

name: Rocbouquet
flavor_text: Beauty that blossoms in an instant is but fleeting. To me, you resemble these fireworks, dream-like and fantastical. So please allow me to engrave in my memory the image of your face as it shines in the bright blooms of the fireworks.
gacha_text: I don't know if we can usher in a new day together, so we should cherish this moment.

name: Mikhail
flavor_text: Attacking the enemy at sunrise is strategically better than making a night attack. First of all, nighttime operations are prone to accidents. Secondly, soldiers are less tired in the morning. And finally, the rising sun will blind the enemy and give us an advantage. All charge!
gacha_text: All charge!
gacha_serif1: Please give us orders!

name: Monika
flavor_text: Fear of death, loss, and the unknown. While I cannot escape these fears, I know they are but mere feelings, and there is nothing more I need to fear.
gacha_text: Good luck, Brother!
gacha_serif1: Katarina, there's trouble!
gacha_serif2: Is there something wrong, Lady Monika?

name: Katarina
flavor_text: I have been charged with protecting Lady Monika as she attends her awards ceremony. This uniform is, of course, for that mission. She demanded it be a little showy... so my outfit's a little... extravagant.
gacha_text: It was your courage, Milady, that ensured our success against Godwin.
gacha_serif1: It was your courage, Milady, that ensured our success against Godwin.
gacha_serif2: As always, thank you, Katarina.

name: Tatyana
flavor_text: You're my only friend. If you leave me here, I'll really be all alone. So please, don't ever, ever, ever let go of my hand.
gacha_text: I'm not running away anymore!
gacha_serif1: I'm used to that.

name: Rukh
flavor_text: I heard tales of creatures like Rukh with four legs. Are they like centaurs? They can't be walking on their hands, crawling everywhere. Ridiculous! We have two legs. Two!
gacha_text: Rukh only has and needs two legs.
gacha_serif1: Now that Big Bro's better, guess I'll head out and see the world.

name: Red
flavor_text: To change into Alkaiser from Red takes only one millisecond, so it's impossible to take a photo of me while I'm changing. That means what you have here is a fake photo. But if this photo is real, then someone's memory is about to be erased.
gacha_text: Now that you all remember me, it's time I go all out!
gacha_serif1: Alkaiser Change!

name: Emelia
flavor_text: Being a spokesperson for an arms dealer is definitely not my thing, because I don't need a gun to shoot you through the heart.
gacha_text: I have work to do.
gacha_serif1: Start

name: Asellus
flavor_text: Even before I accepted the Mystic blood, I was lost. Will I grow up? Will I change? I faced him, and things ended up this way, but I still can't figure it out. Have I grown up?
gacha_text: Another... "me"? Which me would that be?
gacha_serif1: I know this is my fate, and I accept it.

name: Fuse
flavor_text: The name's Lostar. I am an IRPO detective. Just call me Fuse like everyone else. I mean, I've got a bit of a short fuse, but I'm the top member in the Region Patrol. Top in absences, salary advances, number of apology letters... Oh wait, that's not what I meant.
gacha_text: Why'd you shoot him?!
gacha_serif1: He was a friend from my school days, and we knew each other for 10 years. He was always so serious. Unlike me.

name: Princess White Rose
flavor_text: I'm Princess Pumpkin. A pumpkin is much too heavy to wear as a hat, but I think I've done my best to match the motif. I wonder what he would call me if he saw this outfit?
gacha_text: Pumpkins and roses have their ways of life. It pleases me to say that both are wonderful.
gacha_serif1: Just call me White Rose.

name: Elisabeth
flavor_text: I'm not stingy when it comes to showing off my figure. If you want a look, go for it. No big deal. But in exchange, you WILL have to do what I say. Naturally, nothing is free in this world.
gacha_text: Hey, can you put some sunscreen on me?
